#HELPS

0 ARMAGEDDON~
.
   This is a special state where there are no paradox rules or safes for awhile. Hence
people will be able to get as much status as possible depending on how many people they
had decapitated.
~

0 ARENAWATCH NOWATCH~
.
   Use this command to view a participant in the arena and see how they are fighting.
This allows you to see everything they see until the fight is ended.

   If you don't want people to watch you when you are challenging people, use the
#enowatch#n command to stop them too. If you use this but you want people to view you
again in your matches, enter the same command to turn it off.
~

-1 CHANGES~
- transmigration level and class rank is in. SEE HELP TRANSMIGRATION
- can no longer buy training points
- everyone lost the quick recovery from being stunned on the ground (for those who have it)
- HELP 'DUNGEON OF DEATH' is in
- everyone can now use forge. However, you can't forge a weapon whose level is higher than yours.
- runeshift command is also in. This can be used to further customize your equipment.
- you can now specialbuy transmigration levels! 15 gold for 1. You can also win this from betting.
- HELP 'HIDDEN SKILLS' IN! *Sounds corny but hey...*
- The non multi level stock users can now supercancel DM moves using a full bar if they have
  10 or more pkills.
- only normal commanders can use lockon now
- K groove rage mode now gives a 50% damage bonus. It now costs 2/3 of your bar to dodge, counter
  push and supercancel in S groove... and the full bar to retort in S groove. However, the PMAX
  mode for it now gives a 20% damage boost.
- people with lower transmigration now get a offensive and defensive bonus against those who
  have a transmigration level of 1+ million over them. Also for this change, there is now a
  'who transmigration' command that shows all the people that are in your range (of 1 million).
- Dungeon of Death is in. ( Think you are good? Wait till you fight the guardian and jaggar ;) )
- remort Dark Knights lost psychic barrier
- rescue now works properly (ie you rescue the person from whoever is fighting them, NOT who
  they are fighting)
- you now gain your transmigration bonus the SAME TIME as you get the levels. No need to
  reclass anymore. Speaking of which, more reclassing options in.
- everytime you reclass, you need an extra 10 pkills to reclass again.
- monks/ninjas can now eat pktokens again
- overdrive and subsistance are back in with the following changes: You can't have both of
  them on at the same time; overdrive stock bonus + recharge stock bonus doesn't acummulate.
- can now specialbuy lionhearts and betting
- you can now buy transmigration levels with LPs and the maximum transmigration levels you
  can have is 25 million
- reclass people can now fight non-reclass again. If people go back to bitching, the pk will
  be divided again.

- SEE HELP OLDCHANGES
~

0 'LONE WOLF' 'TEAM TRIANGLE'~
.
   This represents the next stage in fun and strategy in the realm of utopia. Now,
players can decide whether or not they want to be a #wlone #owolf#n or form a
#Cpowerful #yteam#n in their pk battles. Each has their own benefits and disadvantages
as follows:

#w#uLone wolf#n

#c- #ghas 200% more defense than team members.
#c- #ghas 33% more offense than team members.
#c- #gCan use the weapon equipment skills.
#c- #gtends to get a better avg agility and tension than team members.
#c- #gGets some mighty demigod powers as pkills go up.

#yTeam triangle#n

#P- #oControl of 3 characters, yes 3 that can be tagged in at any time.
#P- #ohas no timer clashes (since it is 3 characters, not one character with 3 classes)
#P- #ohas their own skillbuy points, deities etc.
#P- #oGet some kool team powers as pkills go up.#n

   Think of a lone wolf like a demigod, like the last boss in a fighting game if you
will and think of the team triangle as a group of normal fighters. The key thing to
note is all three members of a team has to be beaten for you to obtain a 'kill' for
them. Also, to help facilitate this, decapitation will be made auto. Finally, unlike
the normal fighting system now, this will be quite faster. Post your thoughts on
board 1 on if you want it in or not.
~

