- weaknesses are in and HELP 'EQUIP SKILLS' UPDATED
- website updated with a miniforum and plans for a who's online are in the works.
- dragoons can now transform anytime.
- all lvl 2 equip skills + gshield are in
- all lvl 2 and 3 skills but sonicarc, grim reaper and roulette are in
