  discipline. In other words, expect meaner dragoons. (SEE HELP DRAGOON for new files)
- Deities now give you stat penalties and bonuses. See help deities for more details
- Melee bug was fixed and melee overall was improved.
- new equip skills are in, such as lloth (summon), sustain, aragami, etc
- Lvl 4 Skills and Deities bonuses are in. Recheck them. Also, Phoenixes are toned down.
