0 'DUNGEON OF DEATH'~
.
  Every once in awhile, the gates to hell will be revealed to the fighters of utopia.
However, the fear radiating from its opening is so great that only the mightiest of
warriors can venture through them... as a team.
  Inside, you shall be greeted by the halls of no return - a nasty maze fill with
devastating traps and haunting perils. If that wasn't enough, you also have to fend off
the hatred of other teams who also have the same goal as you... being a legend.
  If you manage to make it to the end of each floor, the bosses of terror awaits you...

  #wRequirements:
    #y30 pkills minimum
    #y2 or 3 person group team (3 is HIGHLY recommended)
    #yBattle Smarts (You WILL need it)
    #yGood Luck (Heh, you WILL need this too)#n

#wSEE ALSO: #eHELP 'DUNGEON LEVELS', 'HIDDEN SKILLS'#n
~

