0 TRANSMIGRATION~
.
  Your transmigration level is simply a bonus that is given to your base stats whenever
you get a pkill or reclass. It is done as follows:

#w1 #Rhp #wfor each #Ctransmigration level
#w1 #Cmana and move #wfor each 2 #Ctransmigration levels
#w1 #ytraining point #w(tp) for each #C100,000 transmigration levels#n

  Players get transmigration levels for pkilling other people, eating pktokens, as well
as progressing through the #edungeon of death#n. On average, people gain these
transmigration levels per action:

#weating pktoken - #g15,000 to 25,000 transmigration levels
#wplayer killing - #g25,000 to 35,000 transmigration levels before #C31 #gpkills
               #w- #g45,000 to 60,000 transmigration levels after #C30 #gpkills
#wclass rank     - #g100,000 transmigration levels for each rank (minus 1)

  #pN.B/ If you attack (jump) someone who has a transmigration of 1 million or more below
than you, then he will be given a damage boost of 10%/defense boost of 5% and up
(I.e/ 3 million - 30% O, 15% D, 4 million - 40% O, 20% D, 8 million - 80% O, 40% D ).
So take heed.#n
~

0 FORGE RUNESHIFT~
.
#gForge        #y- #gUse one of your existing equipment to make a new one of your choice.
#gRuneShift    #y- #gCustomize one of your existing equipment with more stats and affects.#n
~

