0 'SKILLBUY DETAILS'~
.
#wKakusu - #oAllows one to hide in the shadows.
#wEyes of the Heavens - #oAllows one to see all but the masters of Kakusu.
#wSuperHeal - #oAn useful technique that restores some of your stats.
#wAbsorb - #oDampens the blow of attacks against you.
#wHitrate - #oIncreases your hitrate.
#wDodge - #oIncreases your parry/dodge.
#wAccelerate - #oMakes your timers recover faster.
#wTimerlock - #oMakes your opponent's timers recover slower.
#wHunt - #oAn enhanced tracking technique used to stalk victims.
#wStealth - #oPrevents tracking and hunting.
#wEncase - #oEnlit your weapon with an elemental property.
#wAura Shield - #oProtect yourself from Encasing affects.
#wPractice - #oIncrease the damage you do by a random %.
#wKnowledge - #oDecrease the damage you take by a random %.
#wPlanar Caller - #oGo in and out Shadowplane/Etherealform at will.
#wShadowGrasp - #oRip someone out of the netherworld... leaving them at your mercy.
#wGodpeace - #oProtect yourself, or others from all forms of attacks.
#wDischard - #oRemove God's protection from a victim, letting them be attackable.
#wCritical - #oA chance for your melee to do extra damage.
#wAnticipate - #oBy always being prepared, you can evade the sudden critical attacks.
#wRetort - #oA chance to counter a melee attack with one of your own.
#wSwerve - #oThe ability to push melee attacks aside occassionally.
#wPower Blow - #oEvery now and then, you can stun a victim with a lucky strike to the head.
#wShock Absorber - #oThe ability to come out of stun (woozy) almost immediately.
#wIllusion Blur - #oYour movements are so fast that you can dodge attacks like a blur. #P(*)
#wWeapon Guard - #oYour enhanced knowledge on weapons allow you to parry better. #P(*)
#wMajesty - #oThe ability to make a room a safe haven to all.
#wDesanctify - #oThe ability to remove the blessings of a room, making it normal again.
#wFocus - #oBy contrentating on your spiritual powers, your mana regeneration is increased.
#wBalance - #oBy being one with nature and the earth, your move regeneration is increased.

#P(*)  - #eSome classes start with this skill.

#CSEE ALSO: HELP 'SKILLBUY DETAILS 2'
~

0 'SKILLBUY DETAILS 2'~
.
#wScorching - #oYour techniques gradually wear down opponent's equipment before breaking them.
#wMaintenance - #oImmunity to all equipment damaging techniques.
#wAssassin Mind - #oImmunity to all 1 hit kill abilities and Luck of the Devil. #P(*)
#wLuck of the Devil - #oImprove chances of the 'chance' skills to work, like 1 hit kills for e.g #P(*)
#wAntiAura - #oTakes away opponent's auras and lagging them in the process.
#wReminisce - #oImmunity from AntiAura and you can now change auras with no lag.
#wPelt - #oDoes as it says, send a person flying out of the room.
#wTrip - #oUseful in countering the throw technique, by lagging and/or stunning players.
#wMime - #oAbility to cast spells without the use of one's voice.
#wSniper Sight - #oBeing one with the darkness, and a traveller of light comes immunity to blindness. #P(*)
#wSteal - #oTake an opponent's items for your own use, with them unawared of your intentions.
#wPresence - #oHave a heightened sense of your surroundings and be more cautious of your goods.
#wShadowSwap - #oUse this to exchange your bad spell affects for your opponent's good ones.
#wMind Control - #oImmunity from ShadowSwap, leaving your spell affects untapped.
#wHelping Soul - #oThis greatly improves all healing skills.
#wLeechingtouch - #oSend leeching spirits at your foe, greatly lowering their healing skills.
#wStunning Blow - #oKnock down any foe with Ryo's father trademark move.
#wRoll - #oCan greatly shorten the time you spend in a stunned state.
#wRigid Body - #oImmunity from SubtlePinch and a slight tension raise.
#wSubtlePinch - #oLower the rate at which the opponent gains stock.
#wSerpent Fist - #oYour techniques drain more of the opponent's block meter than normal.
#wIron Body - #oYour mastery of the body allows you to have 150 block meter.
#wFirst Attack - #oJust about always get first attack.
#wFinal Blow - #oOne last chance to get the opponent down with you to the grave...
#wAnalyse - #oKnow everything about a character, including their strengths, weaknesses... #P(**)
#wDetermine - #oStudy attacks to determine what damage they do, their elemental type, etc... #P(**)
#wDisarm - #oChance of disarming a foe every round. #P(*)
#wGrip - #oImmunity from all disarming techniques. #P(*)
#wSnake Strike - #oImproved Counter Rate.
#wShining Blow - #oNullifies the affect of Snake Strike and lowers counters.
#wStagger - #oUse a secret technique to destance an opponent.
#wSwitch - #oWith the mastery of stances come immunity to stagger and the ability to change at will.
#wFrostbite - #oA low attack that greatly burdens the moving costs of victims.
#wThawing Heart - #oThe ability to come out of freezing attacks almost immediately.

#P(*)  - #eSome classes start with this skill.
#P(**) - #eEveryone can use these skills.
~

