0 DECAPITATE CRACK~
.
    Do this to another player when they are mortally wounded, and you will 
slay them, most likely getting rank if they are in your range. You may also
loot their corpse for gold, of course, and if you are hungry you can even eat 
their head ;)
    Decapitation alone is not enough to completely destroy another player 
however, for their head will retain their remaining lifeforce. To truly 
kill them, you must crack open their head and eat (or in some other way 
destroy) their brain.
~

0 WEATHER~
.
Now that weather affects pkilling with you being constant rangers throughout the
land of #RVOD#n it is vital that you know what you are dealing with. There are four
seasons you have to deal with. #CWinter#n, #ySpring and Summer#n, and finally #0shadow#n
months.

   #C#uWinter Months#n          #y#uSpring and Summer Months#n             #0#uShadow Months#n
     "Winter"                "The Grand Struggle"            "The Dark Shades"
 "The Winter Wolf"             "The Spring"                   "The Shadows"
 "The Frost Giant"               "Nature"                   "The Long Shadows"
  "The Old Forces"              "Futility"                "The Ancient Darkness"
                               "The Dragon"                  "The Great Evil"
                                "The Sun"
                                "The Heat"
                               "The Battle"

The #CWinter#n months is when #7Snowing#n and #LIcestorms#n occurs.
The #ySpring and Summer#n months is when #yLightning#n occurs.
The #0Shadow#n months is when #0Eclipse#n and #RApocalypse#n occurs.

The following affects will be caused by weather:

#cRain - Leaves no tracks.
#yLightning - Lags and hurts the victim.
#CSnow - Always leaves tracks.
#LIceStorm - Chance of freezing you.
#0Eclipse - Darkened affect and special bonus to a class.
#RApocalypse - Can travel anywhere and a special bonus to a class.#n

Remember these features, as one day Ranger, it might help save your life..
~

0 CAPTURE~
.
   The Clan ranking system of Kingdoms are based on Captures. Whenever a player
from one kingdom captures another player from a different kingdom and he is of
the same and less Rank than the victim, He will gain one rank while the victim losing
one, in essence 'stealing it'. As your Ranking goes up, you will have access to more
of your subclan skills.

   Please note that in armageddon, players can't lose Ranking although you can still
gain them.
~

0 INVASION~
.
   To invade a kingdom is relatively simple. Simply find the invasion room
in your kingdom or at recall, then say these magic words... providing you
have no fight timer:

#wCamelot         - #ySay Camelot
#wUnderworld      - #ySay Underworld
#wSOLDIER         - #ySay Soldier#n
~

