0 KINGDOMWARS~
.
   Think your kingdom is IT?! Think you are LEGIT! Then just don't QUIT!! Come and EXHIBIT
your maaaaaad skills in this weekly war of chaos!
   The rules are simple. Have the MOST kingdom kills at the end of the week! Simple huh?
Maybe, for see you can only get them from killing opponent kingdom members!
   So Stopping chatting with your friends, leave that for AIM, clean up the rust, its time
to win some FAME! For if you do not, then you are quite LAME! Thus the punishment you
get is quite far from TAME!
~

