0 'DEMONSKILLS'~
.
#RSin         - #yCurse a victim with the wrath of the devil.
#RDamnation   - #yA psisonic shield that damages all scryers.
#RLavaPit     - #yFill the room with deadly magna, doing vicious damage perodically.
#RFrostBreath - #yBreathe a devastating breath on your victims.
#RDarkHoly    - #ySmite down your foe with the power of Darkness.
#RDesanctify  - #yRemove the safety of any room with the wrath of chaos.
