0 'DEMONSKILLS 2'~
.
   Skills avaliable to powerful demons are:

#RSnake Style - #yA deadly stance perfected by the Orochi himself that allows swaying
              movements of the hands to execute cripple counter attacks. #P(Needed for
              some techs)
#RZombie      - #yTemporary transform a player into a zombie, thus making all healing
              abilities damaging him/her.
#RShed        - #yBy focusing on the snake style, the demon can escape EXTREMELLY easily
              from battle by shedding its skin and leaving it to fight his foes. Take
              note that this also remove -ve affects from him as well.
#RBattleLust  - #yLovers of destruction and senseless fighting, these foul creatures of
              hell had devised a spell that improves the power of themselves and allies.
#RDemonCradle - #yBy focusing on the snake style, the demon can use his perfect body
              to seduce and devastate a foe with a crippling upperslam.
#RCrucifix    - #yJust like Jesus Christ, pin yourself on a wooden cross... but for the
              forces of evil instead of saving mankind.
#RBreakThrough- #yDon't you hate it when people have resilience to your best techniques?
              So do demons so you can guess what this technique does.
#RVenomStrike - #yFear masters of the snake style, for they can use their slippery skills
              to evade techniques and strike back with poisonous fang shaped hands. #P(Auto)
#RDemiProt    - #ySimilar to the Angel's version, but this protects the wear from the
              forces of good.
#REndoZone    - #yPull the earth itself in between the normal and demon realm, where the
              rules of Mankind, nature and the Heavens are disbanded.

Still working on this but expect a nice set of skills
~

