0 'ANGELSKILLS'~
.
   These beings are representatives of the right flank of the divine army. Almost
impossible to look at because of the brilliant light radiating off their body, these
beings quickly destroy their enemies with their swift, but powerful sword techniques.

   Skills avaliable to normal angels are:

#wFistTakedown    - #LA swift Stunning Attack.
#wRedemption      - #LShow fear to the followers of evil, thus immobolizing them.
#wSmite           - #LPowerful Holy Magic which make foes reel back in pain.
#wTrueForm        - #LAbility to turn into a Seraph, leaving your human disguise behind.
#wAngelicaura     - #LThe aura of justice lets you strike down evil. ( Auto )
#wReflection      - #LThe aura of redemption bounces feeble spells back at their casters. ( Auto )
#wGSpirit         - #LSuffer the pain of others by protecting them with your spirit.
#wGShield         - #LEngulf your target with a antiganging shield.
#wHolyBall        - #LA devastating holy attack that drains magical energy.
#wGodpeace        - #LNo harm will come to those protected by God.
#wBlazingHand     - #LEnlit your free hand with purifying flames.
#wHolyWord        - #LSing the praises of God letting his love shatter Evil.#n

#wSEE ALSO: HELP #L'ANGELSKILLS 2'#n
~

0 'ANGELSKILLS 2'~
.
   Skills avaliable to powerful angels are:

#wAngelWings       - #LJust like the Lvl 3 skill, use your wings to stun your foe.            
#wPurification     - #LRemove all -ve affects from the group and give protection from curses.
#wThe Speed of Love- #LEnhanced Travel to those you are protecting. #P(Auto)
#wHoly Guidance    - #LBy utilizing the powerful 'protection from evil' spell, Angels have an edge
                 against those of the dark side.
#wHolyThorns       - #LStore some of the damage down to you while you are protecting others, then
                 lash it back with a devastating spiritual attack. #P(Auto)
#wHolyRetrieval    - #LA spell that brings back people from shadow and etherealplane.
#wSeraphCurse      - #LTemporary make a foe/ally's attacks and techniques non elemental.
#wHope             - #LBy placing one's faith in the Light, anything is possible.
#wSaviour          - #LWith knowledge of being the Avenger comes the power to ignore the pain
                 obtained from protecting others, and use this to heal you instead. #P(Auto)
#wHeavenlyCloak    - #LCover your friends with a technique evading cloak. #P(Next Tech Dodged)
#wGenesis          - #LAtone for your failure by warping time back before everything took place.
#wDivine Judgement - #LPray for God's assistance as you temporary disrupt the chaos and cruelty
                 in the world #P(No Tying or Decapitation).
#wTyrael           - #LAt Death's door, the archangel himself is well known for intervening fights
                 to save his heavenly brothers and sisters. #P(Summon) (Auto)#n
