.
   Although these Holy Beings spend much of their time in Heaven bringing
Glory to the eyes of God, they usualy spend time by themselves developing
their skills.
   Mainly, they focus training on their body, combat and magic capabilities.
   To see what you can learn, type Study by itself then do the syntax that
it tells you to to learn your abilities.

