0 WIZARDS~
.
   Centuries ago, Utopia was a land full of life, magic, wars, trade... everything
that affects the progress of any world. Mages were held in high regard as masters of
the arcane skill of magic. It was considered an art... a science for scholars. However,
after many years, the use of magic changed and that is where are story begins...

#pMagearmor - #cAll followers of magick need this to further their studies.
#pMageTalk  - #cMages communication channel.

#wSEE ALSO: HELP WIZARDSKILLS, WIZARDBLESSES, WIZARDCURSES, WIZARDSPECIALIZATION, WIZARD-ATTRIBUTES#n
~

0 WIZARDSPECIALIZATION~
.
       #C#uBattle Mages#n

#pEvocate           - #cA VERY POWERFUL weapon enchanting skill only capable by the Masters of Magick.
#pAggression        - #cCall forth the eteranl fires to fill your heart with passion.
#pElementalTouch    - #cSmitten your foe with the wrath of the Deities. (Non ArchMage)
#pSoulField         - #cSurround yourself with powerful illusions, that mimicks your every move.

       #C#uSummoners#n

#pDeity Call        - #cAbility to summon any deity the summoner wishes.
#pBriarShield       - #cProtect yourself with magical armor.

       #C#uTime Mages#n

#pAccelerate        - #cAbility to manipulate time around a victim, bringing the future to the present.
#pPrimalRage        - #cLet time flow through nature as you charge up spiritual energy.
#pTimeWarp          - #cFear those who have NO consideration for time itself.
#pQuicken           - #cAbility to hasten the body, lowering the time lag after attacks. (Non ArchMage)

       #C#uBook Mages#n

#pChant             - #cUse your custom made spells to destroy the enemy. They DON'T need anything else.
#pDisempower        - #cMake those who fight against you weaker.
#pAureola           - #cOne of the Legendary weapons that was sealed... until now. #p(30 pkills)

#wSEE ALSO: HELP #o'BOOK MAGES', 'BATTLE LIMITS', 'SUMMONER LIMITS', 'TIME LIMITS', 'BOOK LIMITS'#n
~

0 'SUMMONER LIMITS'~
.
#pMoogle            - #cBring warmth and joy to you and your friends, healing your wounds. #w(Level 1)
#cSalamander        - #pFill the room with the damning flames of the salamander. #w(Level 2)
#pBahamut           - #cThe ultimate summon... for the ultimate summoner. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 'BATTLE LIMITS'~
.
#pTempest           - #cSend deadly shards of Ice onto your foes. #w(Level 1)
#pSummon            - #cSummon a wyrm to fight on your behalf. #w(Level 2)
#pUltima            - #cUltilize the forbidden magic to SMASH all foes to their very knees. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 'TIME LIMITS'~
.
#pStop              - #cAbility to manipulate time around a victim, freezing them at will. #w(Level 1)
#cNatureRevolt      - #pThe wrath of nature... to all foes. #w(Level 2)
#pAge               - #cAbility to disrupt the body, increasing the time lag after attacks. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 'BOOK LIMITS'~
.
#pSpirit Blast      - #cDisrupt a foe with energy from the Netherworld. #w(Level 1)
#pSuper Chant       - #cA powerful damage spell that has to be written. #w(Level 2)
#pUltra Chant       - #cThe ultimate damage spell you can write. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 'BOOK MAGES'~
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
	Reality is up for grabs.
	Magick is the key; Ascension is the goal.  Magick is not dead, no
matter what we make think.  It slumbers beneath the weight of disbelief,
but it is not dead.  In the mists of spirit worlds and the shadows of
hidden sanctums, in the laboratories of the Awakened and the sacred places
of the Dreamers, magick is alive.
       --Phil Brucato, Mage: The Ascension
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
      MLEARN- The ability to learn runes, sigils, and gylphs.
       RUNES- Runes allow a wizard to imbue a spell into paper, allowing
              that spell to be cast for free.
       CHANT- This allows the wizard to chant mystical spells created by the
              wizard.
     GLAMOUR- This allows the wizard to rename his books.

      SEE ALSO: Help 'SUPER ULTRA DAMAGE SPELLS', 'SPELL COMBINATIONS',
                     'SPELL AFFECT EXAMPLE', 'SPELL DAMAGE EXAMPLE'
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
~

0 'SPELL AFFECT EXAMPLE'~
.
#w#uAffect Spell#n

write page line Start.affect.spell
write page line victim.target
write page line apply: hp
write page line apply: mana
write page line apply: move
write page line apply: str
write page line apply: vit
write page line apply: min
write page line apply: spi
write page line apply: dex
write page line apply: eva
write page line apply: agi
write page line apply: ten
write page line bonus: 100
write page line duration: 1000
write page line message.1: You bless $N
write page line message.2: $n blesses you
write page line message.3: $n blesses $N
write page 0 end.page

If you want this to be a curse instead, have this in the 2nd line:
- write page line reversed

#oNB - Note you can only use this when you have 20 pkills and more#n
~

0 'SPELL DAMAGE EXAMPLE'~
.
#w#uDamage Spell#n

write page line Start.damage.spell
write page line victim.target
write page line min.damage: 500
write page line max.damage: 1000
write page line message.1: Bomb
write page line message.2: Bomb
write page line message.3: Bomb
write page line next.page
write page (0-7) end.page


Make sure the next.page line isn't in the LAST (8th) page
If you want this to be a heal instead, have this in the 2nd line:
- write page line reversed

#wSEE ALSO: #oHELP 'SUPER ULTRA DAMAGE SPELLS'#n
~

0 'SPELL COMBINATIONS'~
.
   #w#uRUNE     GLYPH            SIGIL         Affect#n
   #CFIRE   #o+ #CDESTRUCTION    #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wBlaze
   #CAIR    #o+ #CDESTRUCTION    #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wCall Winter
   #CAIR    #o+ #CDESTRUCTION    #o+ #CAREA        #o- #wCall Lightning
   #CEARTH  #o+ #CDESTRUCTION    #o+ #CAREA        #o- #wCall/Remove Waste (20 pkills)
   #CWATER  #o+ #CENHANCEMENT    #o+ #CSELF        #o- #wEnhanced EnergyFlux for anyone
   #CDARK   #o+ #CTRANSPORTATION #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wGlobal curse
   #CDARK   #o+ #CREDUCTION      #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wEnhanced Global Poison
   #CDARK   #o+ #CCONTROL        #o+ #CAREA        #o- #wGlobal Sleep
   #CLIFE   #o+ #CENHANCEMENT    #o+ #CSELF        #o- #wEnhanced Refresh for anyone
   #CLIFE   #o+ #CREDUCTION      #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wGlobal Enhanced Energy Drain
   #CMIND   #o+ #CREDUCTION      #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wGlobal dispel magic
   #CMIND   #o+ #CINFORMATION    #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wGlobal read aura
   #CSPIRIT #o+ #CTRANSPORTATION #o+ #CSELF        #o- #wTeleport to anyone in the world
   #CSPIRIT #o+ #CREDUCTION      #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wGlobal faerie fire
   #CWATER  #o+ #CCONTROL        #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wJail of water (Entomb)
   #CSPIRIT #o+ #CCONTROL        #o+ #CTARGETING   #o- #wSummon/Disperse the Vortex (20 pkills)

   #oMake #w#zsure#n you have all of these stuff learnt in #PMlearn#n
   #oThen you cast major whatever object you need.
   #oAfter that you use c copy *item* page, then c insert page book.
   #oCongratulations on your new spell!#n
~

0 'SUPER ULTRA DAMAGE SPELLS'~
.
   These spells are like normal damage spells but alot more powerful. However,
because of this extra strength, it will take the wizard time to recover from
the casting till he can use them again.

Syntax: Use #ystart.super.damage.spell#n instead of #wstart.damage.spell#n for
        Super spells. ( 8 pages max )

Syntax: Use #ystart.ultra.damage.spell#n instead of #wstart.damage.spell#n for
        Ultra spells. ( 8 pages max )
~

0 WIZARDBLESSES~
.
#pAlabaster Potion - #cDrink this potion to get improved strength.
#pGaeaBlessing     - #cFills one with the blessing of Gaea.
#pCleanse          - #cRemove -ve effects from your body.
#pHaste            - #cMove faster than the speed of sound with this useful spell.
#pMangaraBlessing  - #cMake mortals stronger with the help of this Saint.
#pDivine Wisdom    - #cA blessed spell that increases one hitrate.
~

0 WIZARDCURSES~
.
#pSlow           - #cCast on your foe to slow down their speed.
#pLumica         - #cA very powerful anti-magic field that only bows to the true masters.
~

0 WIZARDSKILLS~
.
#pFireball     - #cA huge magical fireball use to burn foes.
#pEnrage       - #cCauses a target to go ballistic against ALL attackers.
#pDrainPower   - #cSteals your victim's mana for your own.
#pGaseous      - #cPuts a target into/out from the Spiritual Realm.
#pGreatWall    - #cSummons a wall to hinder victim's offensive power.
#pReveal       - #cNothing is hidden from the followers of Magick.
#pLayHands     - #cUse your inner powers to heal your wounds.
#pLivingLands  - #cThe earth awakes to fight by your side. ( Auto )
#pTelekinetic  - #cImprove the damage of your magical shields.
#pAntiMagic    - #cRemoves auras and spellups from target.
#pUnsummon     - #cCounter summons by killing the mobs with age.
#pWhirlWind    - #cSend your group to safety temporarily at an expense of magic.
#pAccelerate   - #cHasten the ticks around a target, lowering their timers etc.
#pMwall        - #cSurround yourself with the forces of nature.
#pLevitate     - #cLevitate yourself in the air by adjusting air molecules with time.#n
~

0 WIZARD-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #c#uBonuses#n

#p- #cMasters of Blesses
#p- #cMagical energy increases with more kills

   #c#uDisadvantages#n

#p- #cNeeds LOTS of mana for their spells
#p- #cCan only wear robes#n
~

0 MONKS~
.
   There is a great misunderstanding that angels represents the Light's
warriors on the mortal realm. In truth and in fact, there is a special of
powerful priests granted unbelievable powers to destroy evil. Being able to
tap into their magical powers more deeply than their Holy brothers, 
monks are known to venture out in righteous battle, striking 
unmercilessly at all forms of evil with their supernatural feats of
strength and dedication.

#wHum         - #CMonks' communication channel.

#wSEE ALSO: HELP MONKABILITIES, MONKCOMBOS, MONKMASTERY, MONK-ATTRIBUTES#n
~

0 MONK-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #C#uBonuses#n

#w- #CMasters of Unarmed Attacks and the Martial Arts
#w- #CBlessed with Holy Magic and Chi Attacks ( More accessible with more kills )
#w- #CExtremely agile, both in speed and reflexes

   #C#uDisadvantages#n

#w- #CPenalize HEAVILY for using weapons
#w- #Ccan only use robes.
~

0 STANCES~
.
   As a warrior's skill in his martial arts improves and if he is dedicated enough,
he will eventually have the knowledge to learn one of the forbidden fighting styles.
Each fighting style have their own strengths and weaknesses and are seen as more
as a link to a warrior's form of fighting than another art in itself.

   The five forbidden fighting styles are:

-    #RRyuukuchi Kouen#n: Art of the Invincible Dragon
-         #wTomoe Nage#n: Art of the Raging Tiger
-        #CHandou Geki#n: Art of the Patient Crane
-  #LShinurai Ninjitsu#n: Art of the Swift Falcon
-        #yKirija Sika#n: Art of the Killer Mantis
-         #oMundus Zen#n: Art of the Hungry Wolf

   To go in the fighting style you want, type #Lstance <Tiger/Crane/Dragon/Falcon/Mantis/Wolf>#n

   SEE ALSO: HELP #R'RYUUKUCHI KOUEN'#n, #w'TOMOE NAGE'#n, #C'HANDOU GEKI'#n,
                  #L'SHINURAI NINJITSU'#n, #y'KIRIJA SIKA'#n, and #o'MUNDUS ZEN'#n
~

0 'MUNDUS ZEN'~
.
   This is the fighting style of the legend... of the "Lone Wolf" Terry Bogard. Older
brother of Andy Bogard, Terry's ambition was to rid the world of his adopted father's killer,
Geese Howard. In doing so, he had experienced things very few mortals can imagine in a cruel,
long journey. Now with stories of his hungry fists shattering even the mightiest of opponents
told at the campside, many warriors and priests alike wonder if they have what it takes...
to be the lone wolf.

#oAdvantages: #yEnhance Dexterity and Mind
#yDisadvantages: #oPenalty to Spirit and Luck

#yStance Affects:
   #wPower Charge    - #yA Shoulder Tackle which can be used to knock away opponents. #C(Auto)
   #wCalculated Risk - #yUse your battle knowledge to increase Counter rate. #C(Auto)

                    #w#uMonks Only#n

#yStance Moves:
   #wPower Charge    - #yA Shoulder Tackle which can be used to knock away opponents. #C(Manual)
   #wPower Wave      - #yA swift projectile that can be sent after an opponent.


#yLevel 1 Desperation Attack:
   #oBuster Wolf     - #yA very deadly attack which ignites the opponent in flames.

#yLevel 2 Desperation Attack:
   #oOverheat Geyser - #yA powerful attack which stuns the opponent for a bit.

#yLevel 3 Desperation Attack:
   #oTriple Geyser   - #yA blinding attack that has the potential of doing MASSIVE damage. #C(AutoGuard)
~

0 'KIRIJA SIKA'~
.
   Quite argubably the most feared stance of them all. Mastered by the Assassin Gato, this
was believed by many priests and archbishops to be the catalyst of the Kuruda Assassins.
Unlike other styles, the teachings for this are not based on Duty, Honour or Pride... but
an intense desire to kill.

#yAdvantages: #eBonuses to nearly all the stats
#eDisadvantages: #yNot very good in any of the advantages it receives like the other stances

#yStance Affects:
   #oEnergy Reversal - #eChi energy used to return a % of the damage done to you back to the victim.
                   #C(Auto)

                    #w#uMonks Only#n

#yStance Moves:
   #oSoulBomb        - #eSacrifice your lifeforce to devastate the vicinity.
   #oPalm Strike     - #eA vicious assault of chi energy.

#yLevel 1 Desperation Attack:
   #oNeck Breaker  - #eThe name itself leaves very little to assumption.

#yLevel 2 Desperation Attack:
   #oHeavenlyPunch - #eUse divine energy to create a ball of antimatter that disrupts
                   anything that moves.#n  

#yLevel 3 Desperation Attack:
   #oFinal Heaven  - #eWhoever is hit by this...#n  
~

0 'SHINURAI NINJITSU'~
.
   Nothing much is known about this style except that it is favoured by Shaolin Monks
who has close ties with the Ninja Clans of the east. But seeing the ninjas don't like
close confrontations, that this branch of fighting will involve similar tactics.

#LAdvantages: #eEnhanced Evasion
#eDisadvantages: #LPenalty on Strength and Dexterity

#LStance Affects:
   #lAnti Shadow - #eUse the effects of Fade to linger in and out of the shadows in battle. #C(Auto)
   #lEnhanced Blow  - #eA damage bonus to first attack. #C(Auto)

                    #w#uMonks Only#n

#LStance Moves:
   #lFade        - #eDisappear into the shadows and bid your time.
   #lEmpty Blow  - #eAn extremely deadly first attack.

#LLevel 1 Desperation Move:
   #lHishoken Rush   - #eOne of Andy Bogard's trademark attacks...

#LLevel 3 Desperation Move:
   #lInnocence       - #eMay you be rewarded a swift death from this unmerciful counter.#n
~

0 'RYUUKUCHI KOUEN'~
.
   An ancient style used by the Shaolin Monks to annihilate their victims with an
array of power moves. An interesting fact of this is that it is mostly female
monks who favour this fighting style. Alot of opponents will snicker when they see
these slender females which their comical expressions on the battle field. But
they normally don't snicker for long...

#RAdvantages: #eEnhanced Strength and Vitality
#eDisadvantages: #RPenaltiy on Evasion and Agility

#RStance Affects:
   #rDragon Pride - #eCarry on the fight even when others crumble. #C(Auto)

                    #w#uMonks Only#n

#RStance Affects:
   #rBody Clench  - #eUse Your tremedous body to send multiple attackers flying. #C(Auto)

#RStance Moves:
   #rDragon Roar  - #eFill the heart of allies with POWER, rapidly increasing their stock/damage.

#RLevel 1 Desperation Attack:
   #rRising Storm    - #eUse demonic energy to send everyone reeling...

#RLevel 2 Desperation Attack:
   #rBlazing Fury    - #eSend everyone in its fiery path catapulting into the air.
   #rRising Storm    - #eUse demonic energy to send everyone reeling...

#RLevel 3 Desperation Attack:
   #rHaou Ko Kou Ken - #eThose who know this move fears its power... #w(GUARD BREAKER)
   #rRising Storm    - #eUse demonic energy to send everyone reeling...
~

0 'TOMOE NAGE'~
.
   Created by the Regenade Monks of the Northen Lands, the Tomoe Nage isn't for the
weak of heart. Requiring alot of concentration, agility and dedication than any
other fighting style, these priests have to forbade their customary calm states
to perfect their art. When the Shaolin Monks heard of this, they had invaded these
regenade's territory in the hope of stamping out of the practice but after many
years of fighting, there was a standoff and the clans once again become great
allies.

#wAdvantages: #eEnhanced Dexterity and Strength#n
#eDisadvantages: #wPenalty on Vitality

#wStance Affects:
   #wHalo Effect - #eExpand more energy into your attack creating a critical effect. #C(Auto)

                    #w#uMonks Only#n

#wStance Moves:
   #wTiger Rush  - #eExpand TREMEDOUS energy to attack a foe FASTER than the speed of light!

#wLevel 1 Desperation Attack:
   #wPummel      - #eStrike down a foe with seemingly endless strikes.

#wLevel 3 Desperation Attack:
   #wMeteorBlast - #eBecome one with the Tiger and raise hell in the vicinity.#n
~

0 'HANDOU GEKI'~
.
   The newest fighting style of the five, The Handou Geki is for those who prefer
to wait patiently for openings. Frowning upon their sister and brother priests,
these monks fancy their footwork over their hands and are normally seen as
bodyguards of high ranking Neonates.

#CAdvantages: #eEnhanced Vitality and Spirit
#eDisadvantages: #CPenalty on Strength and Dexterity

#CStance Affects:
   #cSwan Stance      - #eAn ancient stance that nullifies damage over a specific range. #C(Auto)
   #cChi Breathing    - #eRegen health periodically by becoming one with nature. #C(Auto)

                    #w#uMonks Only#n

#CStance Moves:
   #cPsycho Ball      - #eBlast a foe with Psychic Energy.
   #cPsycho Rush      - #eA move with various uses.

#CLevel 2 Desperation Attack:
   #cButterFly Strike - #eRip apart an opponent with a sword.

#CLevel 3 Desperation Attack:
   #cSwan Dive        - #eLet the entire area witness the call of a true hero.#n
~

0 MONKMASTERY~
.
   Monks have multiple sets of abilities granted to them by God and through
their very intense training. Take heed well in what you divide to use champion.

#wTwirl       - #CUse your mastery of the martial arts to rip a foe's body apart. #w(10 Pkills)
#wKakeio      - #CA blazing set of attacks which will make all fear the Light. #w(20 Pkills)
#wSecretFist  - #CAn ancient chinese arts that disrupts the foe with negative affects. #w(20 Pkills)
~

0 MONKABILITIES~
.
   Monks have multiple sets of abilities granted to them by God and through
their very intense training. Take heed well in what you divide to use champion.

#wGuidance    - #CPray to God for the guidance of driving your fists into your target.
#wVulcanPinch - #CA subtle pinch to the back of the neck that can disrupts foes.
#wFlamingHand - #CEnlit your hand with a destructive flame.
#wBladeGrasp  - #CA powerful disarming technique that is hard to evade.
#wTarget      - #CFocus your actions against whom you so desire.
#wFocus       - #CEnhanced Combo capabilities.
#wIronHammer  - #CUse your inner powers to stun all attackers.

#wSyntax: #CLearn #yAbilities#n

#wSEE HELP: 'HOLY MAGIC', 'MONK CHI'#n
~

0 'HOLY MAGIC'~
.
#wLevel 2 - #CCloak of Life. This power allows the monk to surround his 
or her body with a holy cloak of life, slightly reducing damage.
( Syntax - Cloak )

#wLevel 3 - #CCurse of Allah. With the wrath of the Light upon them, the victim 
of this holy magic have greet needs to fear the followers of Good and its 
emissaries. ( Syntax - Cast 'Curse of Allah' <target> )

#wLevel 4 - #CBlessing of the Saints. This powerful spell protects a target from 
various forms of curses, dued to the divine powers of deceased saints. 
( Syntax - Cast 'Blessing of the Saints' <target> )

#wLevel 5 - #CDivine Ray. Strike down a foe with the wrath of God.
( Syntax - DivineRay )
~

0 'MONK CHI'~
.
#wLevel 2 - #CDemmak. A powerful energy attack which can devastate a victim.

#wLevel 3 - #CChi Tilak. Use your Chi energy to siphon some of your foe's health.
( Syntax - ChiTilak )

#wLevel 4 - #CHealing Touch. This power allows the monk to imbue his target with the 
essence of God, healing his or her wounds. ( Syntax - Healingtouch )

#wLevel 5 - #CDeath Touch. This power allows the monk to give his victim a deadly 
disease which cripples and wounds him or her. ( Syntax - Deathtouch )
~

0 MONKCOMBOS~
.
   Training furiously non-stop everyday, Monks are well known of their 
mastery in the martial arts, but one day all of their masters were killed.
   Faced with a new dilemma, Bishop Stone and Bishop Billy, spending hours upon
hours analysing their foes' fighting style and praying to the Light for guidance,
had devised a new fighting style - the answer to fight the wickeness around
them.
   Congratulating the priests on their new fighting style, Goshen, the ninja 
Grandmaster has bestowed to Stone a special ceremonial sword and forged an 
alliance to battle the evil which possess the world that day.
   As the centuries go by, champions now have the capability to learn all
of the various forms of master arts. Usually, this takes them a very long time
to accomplish but is worth it.
   These fighting style is quite fast and the moves need to be entered rather
quickly, else it wont work. Note that there are alot of combos so keep on
experimenting with your techniques in the name of the Light.

   You can cancel your combo anytime by using the #wskid#n command.

#wFor more in depth information, See the following help: 'MONK TECHNIQUES'#n
~

0 'MONK TECHNIQUES'~
.
#wSoshuu Jinn  - #CKnee, Roundhouse, Sweep, Sidewinder, Sidewinder, Knee, Shin, Roundhouse
#wMangetsu Zan - #CSweep, Sidewinder, Sweep, Knee, Roundhouse, Sidewinder, Knee, Headbutt
#wNanpa        - #CJab, Elbow, Shin, Elbow, Jab, Sidewinder, Knee, Headbutt
#wMyo Suhaten  - #CKnee, Roundhouse, Sidewinder, Sweep, Roundhouse, Sweep, Elbow, Jab
#wGin Sentsu   - #CElbow, Jab, Roundhouse, Roundhouse, Headbutt, Shin, Sweep, SideWinder
#wVulcan Upper - #CElbow, Elbow, Sidewinder, Sweep, Shin, Jab, Roundhouse, Elbow#n
~

0 WEREWOLVES WEREWOLF~
.
   At the beginning of things, Gaia - the world and the spirit that embodies 
it - set all things in a balance that would maintain and encourage life.  
Near the top of this chain of being was humanity, and above them were the 
Garou - the sacred warriors of the spirit. They were appointed to be the 
crusaders against the Wyrm, who spreads its cancer through the humans.  
They are the preservers of the raw essence of life, of nature's diversity 
and purity. They are the Earth's immune system, fighting the disease of 
the Wyrm. They are the werewolves, and they fight and destroy the 
children of the Wyrm ( such as the vampires ) at every opportunity.

#y* Howl          - #oA special channel that only werewolves can understand.
#y* Lunar Touch   - #oTemporary make other people's techniques be Lunar. #P(20 pkills)
#y* Lunar Eclipse - #oHow many times do people whine about the Eclipse? Now see
                  why the werewolves don't. #P(25 pkills)
#y* Lunar Power   - #oLet Luna use your body as a vessel to temporary increase
                  your group's Lunar Elemental powers. #P(30 pkills)

#wSEE ALSO: HELP GIFTS, WEREWOLF-ATTRIBUTES, 'WOLF LIMITS'#n
~

0 WEREWOLF-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #o#uBonuses#n

#y- #oMasters of the RAAAGE ( Gets better with more kills )

   #o#uDisadvantages#n

#y- #oTheir rage can be their death...
~

0 GIFTS~
.
#yShadowplane   - #oVenture to and fro the Realm of Shadows at will.
#yMoonBeam      - #oSmash your enemy with luna energy.
#yClapofthunder - #oStun all in the room with a thunderous clap.
#yPaws          - #oMake a foe feels smaller than he really is, weakening him.
#yDazzle        - #oSmitten a foe with the glory of Gaia.
#yDisquiet      - #oStrike a foe with a sacred curse.
#yQuills        - #oBristle your fur.
#yGnaw          - #oNothing can't keep a werewolf trap forever.
#yClaws         - #oRelease your claws Wolf.
#yFangs         - #oShow off your fangs Wolf.
#yRazorClaws    - #oSharpen your claws even more.
#yWhelp         - #oAnother powerful curse from Gaia. #w(10 pkills)

#wSEE ALSO: HELP 'GIFTS 2'#n
~

0 'GIFTS 2'~
.
#yClenched      - #oPrevent foes from escaping by locking on to their arms.
#yBarrage       - #oUnleash the rage of Gaia on your foes.
#yCannibal      - #oSend a wendigo after a fleeing foe. #w(5 pkills)
#yQuickSand     - #oFills the room with quicksand, preventing easy escape.
#yWaste         - #oTemporary make the vicinity a barren land.
#yLambent       - #oAttempt to blind the room with Gaia's Grace.
#yCheapShot     - #oAt times, get in a few extra hits from your madness.
#yCamoflauge    - #oBlend into your surroundings.
#yBanshee       - #oLet go a devastating howl that leaves everyone reeling in pain.
#yRage          - #oRelease your rage onto the room, transforming into True form.
#yCalm          - #oCalm your rage, slowly going back into human form.#n
~

0 'WOLF LIMITS'~
.
#yTornadoSlice  - #oA vicious attack used to disarrange groups. #w(Level 1)
#oAvalanche     - #yUnleash an icy avalanche on your foes. #w(Level 2)
#ySpiralMoon    - #oSmitten all foes with the power of Gaia. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 VAMPIRES~
.
   For in balance of life, where there is good, there is evil. Evil comes in many
forms but what greater evil is there than the children of the Wyrm. Spreading hideous
act of their devilous ways. For centuries, the vampire roamed the land. These nocturnal,
blood thirsty creatures have lived amoung the human race feeding on them as cattle,
turning innocent into vampires.
   As the human race evolved as time past, the vampire world changed as well.
Vampires are the creatures of the night and thus take damage if exposed to daylight.
Vampires cannot eat food, or drink any liquids except for blood. If they cannot drink
blood for a long duration of time they will start taking damage or maybe even go berserk,
so it's a good idea to store some blood in a drinking container.
Some commands are:

#R* Claws      - #eIncrease damage.
#R* Fangs      - #eGives a free bite attack in combat, and required to 'bite' people.
#R* Vamptalk   - #eA special vampire channel which distinguishes between clans.

#wSEE ALSO: HELP 'VAMPIRE SKILLS', VAMPIRE-ATTRIBUTES, 'LEGEND OF THE SOUL REAVER',
               'VAMPIRE LIMITS'#n
~

0 'LEGEND OF THE SOUL REAVER'~
.
   The most Fabled weapon to ever pass the eyes and hands of a vampire. This weapon is said to
cause massive destruction in the hands of a true fighter. After Jedah Le'Vane's untimely death
at the hands of Tyrael Darkbane, he ordered that his corpse and the glyph be sealed for eternity.
Although the council quarreled over his last request, they went along with it... sealing his
remains inside a sacred place. Some say it is the abyss, others say it lies in the desert
of despair. Only few will ever find the location, and even fewer will survive to behold
its power.

#eSoulReaver - #RSummon the weapon once you have the glyph. The weaker you are, the more it shall
             consume you. #w(10 pkills)

Also, different elemental properties can be given to the reaver. While they won't be the actual
elements themselves, each will have a special purpose/gift.

See: HELP #r'REAVER PROPERTIES'#n
~

0 'REAVER PROPERTIES'~
.
   The Soulreaver is more than your average powerhouse sword/claw. With control over its abilities,
you can change it's properties to better suit your enviroment. The 8 Reavers are: DarkReaver, 
LightReaver, FlameReaver, ChillReaver, StoneReaver, ShockReaver, SoulReaver, and FaithReaver.
   For the vampire to be able to change the properties of his reaver, he has to use the #esoulreaver#n
command.

#eDarkReaver  - ( Syntax: Dark )
#wLightReaver - ( Syntax: Light )
#RFlameReaver - ( Syntax: Fire )
#LChillReaver - ( Syntax: Chill )
#oStoneReaver - ( Syntax: Stone )
#yShockReaver - ( Syntax: Shock )
#CSoulreaver  - ( Syntax: Soul )
#PFaithreaver - ( Syntax: Faith )#n
~

0 VAMPIRE-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #e#uBonuses#n

#R- #eMasters of the Bite
#R- #eAdept in Claws
#R- #eMasters of Illusion and great in dodging ( Gets better with more kills )
#R- #eMasters of Draining Techs ( Gets better with more kills )
#R- #ePowerful vampires can summon the powerful soulreaver

   #e#uDisadvantages#n

#R- #eTakes periodic damage in daytime.
~

0 'VAMPIRE LIMITS'~
.
#RSpiritBlast  - #eA powerful attack that can be used in wolf or bat form. #w(Level 1)
#eSoulStrike   - #RUse a replica of the Reaver to drain life from a foe. #w(Level 2)
#RSoulReaper   - #eImpale foes who decide to cross you with your Soulreaver. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 'VAMPIRE SKILLS'~
.
#RAbduction    - #eSteal control of a mob.
#RLamprecy     - #eStrike victims with your tendrils of darkness.
#RGrab         - #ePush/Pull victims into/out of the shadowplane.
#RVsilence     - #eSilence a room, preventing people from communicating.
#RFlash        - #eSacrifice blood to the serpent gods to become faster/stronger. #w(5 pkills)
#RInfirmity    - #eWeaken victims with this ability.
#RUnveil       - #eAttempts to read into a victim's mind.
#RChange       - #eChange into different forms.
#RShroud       - #eDarken an entire area. #w(10 pkills)
#RMajesty      - #eMake any chaotic zone the embody of peace.#n

SEE: HELP 'VAMPIRE SKILLS 2'
~

0 'VAMPIRE SKILLS 2'~
.
#RIllusion BLur- #eMove so fast to evade attacks that it appears you aren't at all. (Auto)
#RRenew        - #eRestore yourself by worshipping the Serpent Gods. #w(5 pkills)
#RDrain        - #eSteals victim's life for your own.
#RMirror       - #eMake clones of yourself to confuse your victims.
#RSpit         - #eSpit venomous acid into victim.
#RTears        - #eSacrifice yourself to the Serpent Gods to save your friends.
#RStigmata     - #eCause your opponent to live the death of the fallen. #w(5 pkills)
#RMaelstrom    - #eSummon a psychic storm on your foes. #w(10 pkills)
#RPsychicCrush - #eBlasts victim. #w(10 pkills)#n
~

0 DRAGON DRAGONS DRAG~
.
     [ Dragons ]
        { 0 }     Dragons once used to rule the realm of mankind.  Unfort-
         |-|      unately, man's fear of the different and powerful caused
         |\|      man to engage in a crusade to destroy and eliminate these
         |\|      powerful and mystical creatures.
         |\|      As each day went by, the population of dragons quickly
     /---------\  declined.  The powerful council of dragons decided that
     |_________|  the only way for the race to come close to surviving was to
         |o|      cross breed with mankind.
         |=|      The new cross breeds were thought to be the final answer but
         | |      the cross breed was the final blow for the race of dragons.
         | |      These new cross breeds possessed the mystical power to
         | |      transform into dragons yet, be accepted by mankind in their
         | |      human form.
         | |      The last of the Elder Dragons, Vaevictis could forsee the
         | |      end of the race of the purebreds.  As a result, he used
         | |      a powerful dragon spell to prevent the newer cross breeds
         \ |      from ever aging like their predecessors and thus never
          \|      ever able to become as powerful.


        #wFor More Info on Dragons check: #eDRAGONPOWER, #rDRAGONAGE, #yDRAGONSKILL
           #cDRAGONCOMBAT, #wDRAGONSHIFT, #bROAR, #eDRAGONGIFT, #oDRAGON-ATTRIBUTES,
           #w'DRAGON LIMITS'#n
~

0 ROAR~
.
   This is the dragon channel.
~

0 DRAGONSHIFT~
.
   Use this to change into your Dragon Form, greatly improving your powers.
~

0 DRAGONGIFT~
.
   This is how the new dragons learn their new powers.

   #oSyntax: #PDragongift <option>
~

0 DRAGONPOWER~
.
   A Dragon's power lies in their dragon form. In dragon form, they have
enhanced armor, toughness, power, and magic.

    #P[ General Abilities for a Dragon ]
    #oClaw         - #PExtract and retract your claws at will.
    #oFangs        - #PExtract and retract your fangs at will.

    #P[ Standard Attributes for a Dragon ]
    #oDragon Armor - #PReduces the damage done to a dragon in combat.
    #oDragon Tough - #PReduces the chance for limbs to get chopped off.
    #oDragon Power - #PIncreased the amount of damage a dragon can do in combat.
    #oDragon Magic - #PEach level allows a dragon to shift to a different dragon
                   form.  The higher this level, the better a dragon has a
                   chance of casting spells in combat.#n

   Similar to their predecessors, the new dragons can acquire slight age
bonuses. The age bonuses results in minor damcap bonuses but the older a dragon
gets, the harder it is for him or her to gain dragon points. The powerful dragon
curse also prevents a dragon from aging normally.  If a dragon isn't in a pre-
sence of danger, it doesn't gain age. 
~

0 DRAGON-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #P#uBonuses#n

#o- #yMasters of the Claw
#o- #yEnhanced regen rate
#o- #yGreat Defense
#o- #yAbility to gain extra hp as kills increase

   #P#uDisadvantages#n

#o- #yAre quite slow.
~

0 DRAGONAGE~
.
   A dragon possesses a different aging system from that of a normal human.
As a dragon reaches certain ages, he will attain a new title. As a dragon
gets older, he or she also receives certain minor bonuses.

#PThe titles are as follows:
    #oHatchling      = #Pyounger than 11 dragon years.
    #oFledgling      = #P11 - 50 dragon years.
    #oJuvenile       = #P51 - 90 dragon years.
    #oYoung Adult    = #P91 - 125 dragon years.
    #oAdult Dragon   = #P126 - 250 dragon years.
    #oAncient Dragon = #P251 - 500 dragon years.
    #oElder Dragon   = #P501 - 750 dragon years.
    #oWyrm           = #P751 dragon years and older.#n
~

0 DRAGONSKILL~
.
   In dragon form, a dragon can use or manipulate certain powers.

   #P[ Auto Dragon Skills ]
     #oDragon Swoop - #Pallows a dragon to swoop down on an unsuspecting target
                    in the same area.
     #oDragon Tail  - #Pallows a dragon to grow a tail in dragon form.
     #oDragon Sight - #Pallows a dragon to see beyond the normal.
     #oDragon Wings - #Pallows a dragon to grow wings to gain flying.
     #oDragon Immunity - #Pallows a dragon to develop protection to poisons.
     #oDragon Fury - #Pawakens the raw power of a dragon.
     #oDragon Intuition - #Pallows a dragon to sense incoming danger.

   #P[ Standard Dragon Skills ]
     #oDragon Breach - #Pprotect yourself from attacks. #y(#wBreach#y)
     #oDragon Breathe - #Pallows a dragon to breathe certain elemental attacks
                      in certain forms.#n
~

0 DRAGONCOMBAT~
.
   In dragon form, a dragon needs to remain active. The success in combat depends
on a dragon's attacking skill and balance.  A dragon has various weapons in
his arsenal of deadly attacks.  A dragon can use attacks such as a deadly high
claw to the effective reliability of a powerful shoulder rush. The attacks are:

#oHigh Claw     - #PSyntax: Highclaw
#oTail Sweep    - #PSyntax: Tailsweep
#oShoulder Rush - #PSyntax: Shoulderrush
#oDragon Breath - #PSyntax: Dragonbreath ( need to learn this )
#oDragon Stomp  - #PSyntax: Stomp
#oHyper Drive   - #PEntice your party's feelings, making them gain more stock. (15 pkills)
~

0 'DRAGON LIMITS'~
.
#oHyperClaw     - #PA swift, but deadly version of the Highclaw. #w(Level 1)
#PMegaFlare     - #oPowerful attack that devastates all. #w(Level 2)
#oFinalFlare    - #PUltimate breathe attack. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 PALADINS~
.
   Paladins are warrior priests who draw their power from acts of righteousness
and strict adherence to the Code of The Temple of Solomon.  Their strength
in battle, combined with the ability to perform limited miracles is offset
by the difficulty they experience in perfecting their craft, and the penalties
they suffer when they stray from the path of good. Bestowed as the protectors
of the Word, they are blessed by the Light to defend the Holy Churches and
spread the praise of God.

#yCommands for the Knights are:

#wPraise         - #oKnight communication channel.
#wHoly Abilities - #oPowerful Techniques blessed by God.
#wPGrant         - #oThe Command to learn the Knight's abilities.

#y*Knights also have the power to summon a Holy war-horse to aid them in battle.

#wSEE ALSO: HELP AURAS, 'HOLY ABILITIES', 'HOLY LIMITS', #yPGR#wA#yNT#w, 'THE AVATAR', 
          PALADIN-ATTRIBUTES, 'HEAVENLY KNIGHT'#n
~

0 'HEAVENLY KNIGHT'~
.
#wGuard - #gAn advanced Shield Block which can be done when the grace of God allows
        it, the Heavenly Knight can use their shield to block #pANY#g attack,
        completely nullifying the damage which the Knight would had received.

#wShellBlast Stab - #gA powerful sword technique which has the power to destroy the
                  target's armor.

#wHellCry Punch - #gA powerful sword technique which has the power to destroy the
                target's headwear.

#wBlaster Punch - #gA powerful sword technique which has the power to destroy the
               target's weapon.

#wIceWolf Bite - #gA powerful sword technique which has the power to destroy the
                target's neckwear.#n
~

0 PALADIN-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #w#uBonuses#n

#y- #wMasters of the Sword
#y- #wMasters of the Shield and Defense ( more Vitality with kills )
#y- #wHave a GREAT passion for Justice. ( obtain with kills )
#y- #wMasters of the Divine Auras ( obtain with kills )

   #w#uDisadvantages#n

#y- #wPowerful techs are very taxing.
~

0 PGRANT~
.
   PGrant is the command to learn Knight's abilities.
   When you type #ygrant#n by itself, you will see a list of things you can learn.

   To learn a sword ability, like Stasis Sword, type #cGrant sword '<sword name>'#n
         For e.g #rGrant 'Stasis Sword'#n

   To learn one of the other abilities, like Honour Gate, type:
        #cGrant abilities <last word of ability>#n
        For e.g #rGrant abilities gate#n
~

0 'HOLY ABILITIES'~
.
   Paladins are well known of their holy abilities. To see the list of techniques to 
learn, type #cPGr#wa#cnt#n. Some of the abilities a Paladin can learn are:

#wGodlySight    - #oThe Ability for a Paladin to see with increased senses.
#wGodsSearch    - #oThe Ability for a Paladin to search on someone in the world.
#wGodsHeal      - #oThe Ability for a Paladin to pray to God to heal their wounds.

#wStasisSword   - #oIcy Sword which may freeze enemies.
#wLightningStab - #oElectrifying Sword which may mute enemies.
#wCrushPunch    - #oSpiritual Sword which drains life force from victims.
#wSplitPunch    - #oHuge Spiritual Sword that has a chance of dealing mortal blows.
#wHolyExplosion - #oBeam of Light which may drive a victim mad for a short while.
~

0 'HOLY LIMITS'~
.
#wSoulHammer    - #oA holy hammer that eradicates the undead. #w(Level 1)
#oFlashSword    - #wShow the unbelievers the power of the Light. #o(Level 2)
#oNoMercy       - #wShow the infideals no... mercy... #o(Level 2) #w(Crusader Only)
#wEruptionSword - #oWatch the unbelievers burn in the flames of truth. #w(Level 3)
#oDemonSlice    - #wSmite down your foe with darkness. #o(Level 3) #w(Crusader Only)
~

0 'THE AVATAR'~
.
   From the beginning of time where chaos spreads over the lands with it evil,
the people needed a champion, a person whose very actions defined the virtues -
Honesty, Compassion, Valour, Justice, Sacrifice, Honour, Spirituality and
Humility. Not many people could be this man, for their lot was occupied with
affairs of the state and other matters. The people needed someone to pursue
these virtues without rest, under the spectre of constant failure. They needed
an image of themselves. They needed the Avatar.
Noone knows the true purpose of the Avatar's quest, but they do know that he is
was very powerful entity who defies all evil and trimuphs good... After his death,
his powers was spread over aspiring crusaders throughout the lands, so they can
continue in his footsteps... so they can be the... Avatar.

Commands available to the avatars are:

#wAvatar        - #oTransform into a replica of the legendary Warrior.
#wCover         - #oProtect an ally, even at the expense of your Life.
#wNemesis       - #oA mysterious attack that is feared by all.
#wGenesis       - #oNothing is known about this attack except that it is a forbidden one...
#wJusticeCutter - #oSacrifice your health to slice through the foe's body. #w(5 Pkills)
#wHand Of God   - #oThe holiest of warriors strike at evil with God's Wrath. #P(Auto) #w(10 Pkills) #P*
#wCharge        - #oPlace your faith in God and rush into battle. #w(10 Pkills)
#wSubdue        - #oStrike at a foe's vital area dampening their next attack. #w(20 Pkills)
#wHolyShield    - #oSummon forth the legendary replicas used in the past. #w(20 Pkills) #P***
#wVengeance     - #oUse this prayer for the forces of Good that was fallen. #P(Auto) #w(25 Pkills)
#wDurandal      - #oGod's greatest gift to the warrior of the Light. #w(30 Pkills) #P**

#P*   - Requires over 749 align and that the paladin's vitality is greater than dexterity.
#P**  - Needs to be mounted for this attack.
#P*** - Shield Block and Bonus to Guard Instance of happening. Note that each successful
      block with this shield will temporary raise vitality by 1 (accumulative).
~

0 AURAS~
.
   During the mid-twelfth century, in the middle of the Age of the Damned, the Holy
Church had decreed that the Divine Word of God would be spread throughout the known
world in order to redeem the masses, Thus, the Church selected a group of its most
charismatic and devoted priests and sent them on a mission to proselytize the 
unfaithful.
   Unfortunately, these priests were not prepared for the rigors of travels or the
hazards of the world. Close to the end of their journey, all of the priests were
captured by a cult and were sacrificed one by one to the Demons. At the last second,
one priest had escaped and returned to the Grand Catheral telling his story.
   In retaliation, the ArchBishop had set about training Holy Warriors to
accompany and safeguard their missionaries. In a further move, he also had the 
priests themselves train in the martial arts of self-defense and this is how the 
first paladins and monks came into being.
   Fully prepared now, the Monks and Paladins were sent on a holy mission to convert
or destroy the cult which had slaughter their brothers. The Head of this party was
Shast Mistargia, a powerful monk, and Lady Ray Mistargia, Grand Paladin of the Holy
Church. As they traveled through the lands to their destinations, they had impressed
the masses with daring deeds, powerful weapons, and martial prowess which were far
more convincing and aspiring than the condemnations of soft spoken words.
   However, after converting most of the people with the Spreading of the Word, and 
destroying all evil in their path, the "Protectors of the Word" and the Monks faded
from public view, wanting no honour or favor for their good deeds. As a result of
this, God blesses them with the Power of the 'Light' - An aura of holy energy with
the Word of God flowing through. With the light radiating off them, Paladins and
Monks had accomplish feats which had the greatest of warriors fleeing in sheer
terror. Dued to their traits and abilities, only paladins continue to rely on these
precious gifts of God.

SEE ALSO: #w'INNER AURA', #r'OUTER AURA', #c'AURAS OF BLESSED DESTINY',
          #g'AURAS OF PEACEFUL AMMENDITY', #w'AURAS OF HOLY PATHS',
          #e'AURAS OF CURSED RAGE'#n
~

0 'OUTER AURA' 'INNER AURA'~
.
   Unique to Paladins, Auras project a field of influence around the caster.
At later levels, any allied character, hireling or minion will benefit from the aura
so long as they are within the immediate vicinity. If the caster is using an aura,
observers will see them surrounded by an aura of blinding light.
   After hundreds of years of use, the paladins had splited their auras into
an outer and inner layer, thus being able to have two affects at the same time.
   With the inner layer, the caster can have it one level higher than possible while
the outer layer of the other aura remains the same. Also, the caster may wish to have
just one aura, increasing its power to 2 levels higher than normal.

   Be wary though, Dued to the sheer force of the light, the caster is limited to the
auras they are capable of learning. In doing holy deeds and spreading the Word throughout
the lands, the caster may be blessed by God to learn new auras, or improve the existing
ones he has before.
~

0 'AURAS OF BLESSED DESTINY'~
.
   Fueled by their zeal and blessed by the Light, Paladins wield powerful skills made
possible only through years of devot dedication and sacrifice. Long campaigns in the
Crusades assisting their brothers the monks have further tempered their abilities,
honing them to razor sharp manifestations of the will of the Light.
   Concentrating on a more offensive manner, the Light has granted the Paladins and Divine
Knights the following auras:

Might - Caught up in the fervor of battle, the Paladin calls upon the power of 
        righteousness and the strength of justice to add force to the attacks of his
        party. what would be glancing blows now strike their mark, and otherwise deflected
        strikes rend through armor to bite flesh.
        #cEffect: Increases damage of these members.#n

Concentration - Those within the sphere of influence of this skill gain the gift of
                clarity. A seren sense of lucidity eases the minds of those within, giving
                them the freedom to focus on individual tasks despite the chaos and 
                distractions of battle. This sense of tranquility allows the Paladin and
                his comrades to strike their blows which would normally bounce off their
                victim's armor.
                #cEffect: Lowers the chance of your party members' attacks to be absorbed
                        by victim armor (not to do with blocking rates) and raise their
                        dexterity.#n

Holy Fire - With a hint of brimstone in the air, the noble Paladin strides into battle
            encased in this holy aura. All those within its range are burnt with the fires 
            of divine virtue. Beware, Beasts of Hell! The fires of purification is upon
            you!
            #cEffect: Periodically does Fire Damage to nearby enemies. Triple damage to
                    those weak vs Fire.#n

See help #w'AURAS OF BLESSED DESTINY 2'#n for the rest.
~

0 'AURAS OF BLESSED DESTINY 2'~
.
Holy Freeze - Using this aura, the Paladin causes the temperature of the air around him to
              drop drastically, freezing the flesh of his enemies. Those so affected may
              find themselves slower, using more energy to defend themselves against the
              upcoming attacks which will send them to their graves.
              #cEffect: Periodically does Cold Damage to nearby enemies. Triple damage to
                      those weak vs Ice.#n

Holy Shock - A Paladin blessed with the power of this aura calls upon the power of the Light
             to strike forth at all enemies surrounding him. Divine bolts spring from the
             earth to smite and sometimes stun the Paladin's enemies.
             #cEffect: Periodically does Lightning damage to nearby enemies. Triple damage
                     to those weak vs Thunder.#n

Thorns - An eye for an eye is sometimes not enough. Those who would strike the emissaries
         of the light had best take warning, for retribution shall be swift and certain. The
         might of your blows may be felt a hundrend fold upon you!
         #cEffect: Enemies take damage when they cause melee damage to party members.#n

Sanctuary - This aura causes the Paladin to shine with an inner, holy light. This light is an
            anathema to beings and users of the undead. This aura carries with it the essence 
            of life and the strength and purity of the Paladin's convictions.
            #cEffect: Periodically does damage and (sometimes) stuns. Triple damage
                    to Mobs and some unknown beings.#n

Conviction - It is fearsome enough to behold the power of a Paladin, yet alone a Paladin aglow
             with the aura of Conviction. This halo of righteousness demonstrates, with force,
             the grim determination of those who shine within it brillance. any who stand 
             against the Paladin and his allies will understand the meaning of folly.
             #cEffect: Reduces blocking capabilities of enemies and increases allies attacks.#n
~

0 'AURAS OF CURSED RAGE'~
.
   They say the light has a darker side... a side most carefully sealed by the divine
forces for eons... protected by the army of heaven for infinity until the invasion
by the Demon of Elru... ID...
   Unable to safeguard this savage form of the light any longer, ArchAngel Tyrael
had banished this light into the abyss... never thought to be hear again until now...
   Found and wielded by the undead knights, this light fills it victim's with
unbelievable power and draw fear even to the mightiest of warriors who dared
oppose it.
   The Dark Side of the Light has bestowed the Undead Knights the following auras:

Life Tap - This skill allows the Undead Knight to literally suck the life from
           his victims. The Undead Knight is able to reach into the wellspring
           of mortality and siphon of its essence, consuming it to replace his
           own.
           #cEffect: Periodically steals health/mana from your attackers.#n

Dim Vision - Damning an enemy to the darkness of their own evil, this curse
             surrounds the afflicted in a sphere of perfect darkness and silence,
             blinding them. This allows a Undead Knight and his party to easily
             evade attacks that may had otherwise connected.
             #cEffect: Decreases victim's hitrate and raise evasion#n

Bone Shield - This aura summons a barrier created from the bones of fallen foes.
              The aura revolves around the Undead Knight, protecting him against
              some attacks.
              #cEffects: A protective shield that absorbs damage and raise vitality.#n

See Also: Help 'AURAS OF CURSED RAGE 2'
~

0 'AURAS OF CURSED RAGE 2'~
Amplify Damage - This deceptively potent curse advances the age and putridity of
                 any wound. Ordinary blows will cut through flesh and carve
                 particularly vicious wounds that fester and seethe.
                 #cEffects: Increases the amount of damage the victims received.#n

Iron Maiden - Wielders of this powerful aura attempts to strike back at the victim
              who dealt damage to them through magical means. The more potent the
              undead knight is, the more certain the counter attack will be.
              #cEffects: Increase chances of counter attacks when the defender gets
                       strucked.#n

Weaken - This bane allows the Undead Knight to sap the strength from his enemy.
         Enemies are enfeebled to the point that their blows become highly
         ineffective.
         #cEffect: Decreases the damage the target can do.#n

Rage - This aura fills the target with an unnatural fury, allowing them to get
       in more attacks at any given time than physically possible.
       #cEffect: Increases the strength and number of attacks the target and his group
     can do but lower their evasive capabilities#n
~

0 'AURAS OF HOLY PATHS'~
.
   They say the light is at its most powerful from its origin and whose to argue with
the forces of heavens? While not as well known as the auras used by mortals, this
ancient side of the light shows no remorse to those who stand against it.
   Blessed from God, the Light has granted the Angels the following auras:

Divine Healing - Purity of the Heart of the persona, subtle is the will of their
                 choiced. Praying for forgiveness and for the strength to carry on
                 their holy mission, angels can be blessed with the power to regen their
                 phyical and spiritual energy much quicker than normal.
                 #cEffects: Periodically restores Hit points, mana and moves to all
                          party members#n

Cleansing - Chaste is the angel in the face of all temptations. Pure in body and spirit,
            he trusts to the splendor of the Light to rid him of all impurities. A
            being of heaven shall neither be tainted, nor corrupted. Thus is the will
            of God.
            #cEffect: Remove all negative affects for all party members periodically#n

Blessed Aim - The spirits of the Light are ever vigilant, and in times of great need,
              have been known to aid their loyal disciples in subtle ways. when this
              aura is enabled, these spirits work to guide the hand of the angel and
              his companions, striking true where blows would normally miss.
              #cEffects: Chances of attacks #umissing#n#c are lowered dued to an
              increase in Mind#n

Blessed Strength - Being able to tap into these unknown resources more than their
                   mortal brothers, angels have the capacity of using the light to
                   perform devastating attacks, rinding away armor and striking bone
                   where normally a mere scratch would had occured.
                   #cEffect: Increases damage dealted by party members as well as 
                             strength of these members.#n

      See help #w'AURAS OF HOLY PATHS 2'#n for the rest.
~

0 'AURAS OF HOLY PATHS 2'~
.
Blessed Speed - Fear the forces of heavens. In their neverending struggle against
                the forces of evils, the beings of heavens had developed a technique
                which allows them to recover from their mystical abilities faster.
                #cEffect: Lowers the waiting time of recovering from equipment based
                        techniques by raising agility.#n

Redemption - An angel must be true to his duty and belief that all souls are worthy
             of forgiveness, even in the face of terrible odds. With this aura, the 
             angel shares the glory of the light with his brave allies. With each
             administration of these final rites, the Angel and his party are redeemed
             physically as well as spiritually.
             #cEffect: Periodically restore stats based on the odds against you#n

Defiance  - Trust in the glory of the Light, for its authority supercedes all power
            in the moral world. With this aura, the angel calls upon the Light to
            protect his allies from harm and death.
            #cEffect: Increase spirit and gives a last resort to all party members#n

Faith - The true word of Light. Armed with the Faith of his consequences and beliefs,
        a follower of the light can perform miracles. Indeed, to the believer,
        anything is possible.
        #cEffects: The more beaten up a party member is, the harder they are to kill#n
~

0 'AURAS OF PEACEFUL AMMENDITY'~
.
   Unlike their powerful brothers, Champions choose the passive side of the Light to help
them in their conversion of the masses. Throughout long campaigns in the Crusades,
champions had filled the people with an impossible aspiration, daring them to do the
undone with the blessed guidance of the Light.
   Concentrating on a more defensive manner, the Light has granted the Champions the
following auras:

Prayer - With this aura, the Champion basks himself and all he deems faithful in a warm,
         healing light. His prayers for salvation carry him through the direst situations,
         allowing him to heal even the deepest wounds in time.
         #cEffects: Restore physical (hp) energy to all friends in the immeditate vicinity.#n

Meditation - With the observance of this aura, the Champion supplicates himself to the Light
             with silent utterances of prayers. It is in these times of silent worship
             that the Champion is rejuvenated in spirit.
             #cEffects: Restore magical (mana) energy to all party members.#n

Resist Earth - Shielding himself and nearby companions within a glow of holy light, the priest
               girds himself against the harsh elements of the earth. By standing resolute and 
               earnest in the face of opposition, his faith is his shield against harm.
               #cEffects: Lowers earth damage to all party members.#n

Resist Fire - Shrouding himself in his devotions, the fervent servant of the Light can walk
              lake of fire and feel only the comforting warmth of his convictions. A Champion
              can even withstand the might of #rMerton#n if his piety is strong enough.
              #cEffects: Lowers fire damage to all party members.#n

See help #w'AURAS OF PEACEFUL AMMENDITY 2'#n for the rest.
~

0 'AURAS OF PEACEFUL AMMENDITY 2'~
.
Resist Cold - The splendor of absolute devotion is all the warmth and comfort a servant of
              God requires. Embraced deep within the shelter of this aura, the faithful
              need never fear the frost.
              #cEffects: Lowers ice damage to all party members.#n

Resist Thunder - Not even the elements of nature can withstand to glory of the Light. When 
                 a follower of God has manifested this aura, he and his allies undergo a
                 lessening of their body's natural conductivity, protecting them from all
                 forms of electricity.
                 #cEffects: Lowers lightning damage to all party members.#n

Vigor - A servant of God feels the rapture of his salvation at all times. In his need, the
        weight of the world lifts from his shoulders, allowing him to march forth to holy
        battle without heed to the lamentations of his body, blocking attacks which may
        not normally be parried.
        #cEffects: Increase Block Rate and Vitality to all party members.#n

Fanaticism - True faith can cause it believers to perform fantastic feats. With this aura,
             the Champion, and all those allied with his cause, carry themselves with a zealous
             fervor, allowing them to strike down their foes as swiftly as the scythe reaps
             the harvest.
             #cEffects: Increase the Hit rate and Dexterity for all friends in the immeditate
             vicinity.#n
~

0 NINJAS~
.
   Ninja, the #eshadow warrior#n, the assassin that puts fears into the hearts
of even their greatest foes.  The ninja has always been a secret society of
assassins and so it is here in #wUtopia#n.  They don't possess supernatural or
mystical powers but they have been known to accomplish miracluous feats
of grace and superb fighting prowess.  Ninjas rely on their combat training
as well as their ancestral knowledge of ninja heritage.

#0Miktalk         - #RNinja Channel.
#0Wuden           - #RThe empty hand combat form that makes the ninja clans so feared.

#wSEE ALSO: HELP PRINCIPLES, NINJITSU, NINJA-LIMITS, NINJA-ATTRIBUTES, WUDEN,
               SCROLLS#n
~

0 NINJA-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #e#uBonuses#n

#y- #LVery high evasion
#y- #LUnbelievable fast

   #e#uDisadvantages#n

#y- #LFairly Weak in the middle of battle
#y- #LPenalize HEAVILY for using weapons
#y- #Lcan only use robes.
~

0 NINJITSU~
.
#0InClimb      -#RInClimb         #0-  Scale nearby walls to your escape.
#0Dig          -#RDig             #0-  Hide yourself in the earth totally unseen for awhile.
#0Incapitate   -#RIncapitate      #0-  Temporary disable a foe's arms.
#0SonicStrike  -#RSonic Strike    #0-  Strike at a foe at the speed of light.            
~

0 NINJA-LIMITS~
.
#eStardance       - #RA star throwing berserking frenzy. #w(Level 1)
#RRisingTiger     - #eThe ultimate ninjitsu combo. #w(Level 2)
#eSplitStrike     - #RAppear to be hundreds of merciless assassins. #w(Level 3)
#eInnocence       - #RMay you be rewarded a swift death from this unmerciful counter. #w(Level 3)#n
~

0 PRINCIPLES~
.
   A ninja learns his art form by following certain principles.
Principles are special powers that a ninja learns. The principles
that are taught are #bS#wo#br#wa#n, and #bN#ei#bn#eg#be#en#bn#eo#n.

#wSEE HELP #bS#wO#bR#wA#w, #bN#eI#bN#eG#bE#eN#bN#eO#n
~

0 SORA~
#wSora        - The Art of finding, observing, and locating principles.#n

#0Koryou      -#RConsider   #0-  Read aura, learn more about your enemies.
#0Uro-Uro     -#RSilent Walk#0-  Leaves no footprint shown behind.(Auto)
#0Kanzuite    -#RAwareness  #0-  A sacred vision that sees all.
#0Bomuzite    -#RSleep Gas  #0-  A gas that makes your enemies go to sleep.
#0Trip        -#RTrip       #0-  Trips their opponent.
#0Mizotamouyo -#RShadowwalk #0-  You are able to walk the paths of darkness to reach another's location.
#0Yoga        -#RCleanse    #0-  Exerts a chinese stance to cleanse your body.#n
~

0 NINGENNO~
#wNingenno    - The Art of attacking and getting away from battle.#n

#0Hakunetsu   -#RFirst Strike  #0-  Super backstabbing attack in the midst combat.
#0Mienaku     -#RVanish        #0-  Never fail flee.
#0Shiroken    -#RThrowing Star #0-  Extra attacks in combat. ( Auto )
#0Dokuyaku    -#RPoison        #0-  Adds poison to your Shiroken. ( Auto )
#0Dinichi     -#RNerve Touch   #0-  Stagger a foe with a powerful ki attack.
#0Orimasu     -#RHeal Touch    #0-  Quickly heal your wounds with this useful tech.#n
~

0 WUDEN~

#wWuden#n is the empty hand art form that the ninjas used to fight.  It has been taught 
for years and passed from one ninja to another.  Every ninja must train hard to perfect each
of the techniques listed below.

#yThrustkick        Spinkick        NKnee        Backfist        Reversesweep
#yUppercut          Lowkick         NSweep 

When a certain combination of these attacks is executed a ninja can execute a certain special
move.  Each special move has it's own properties and tends to work better under certain 
conditions.  The #wWuden#n techniques is based on many of the fighting qualities found in animals
and the ninjas tap in the spirits of certain animals to gain these qualities. 

SEE ALSO: HELP 'WUDEN COMBOS'
~

0 'WUDEN COMBOS'~
.
The legendary combos ninjas can perform are:

#R(Dragon)#e  Dragon Wave - Uppercut, NKnee, Backfist, Spin, Uppercut, NSweep
#g(Snake)#e   Dolphin Kick - Thrust, Spin, NSweep, Backfist, Lowkick, NKnee
#w(Tiger)#e   Hand Swerve  - Lowkick, NSweep, Thrust, NKnee, Reverse, Backfist
#L(Crane)#e   Shindo-Rappa - NKnee, NKnee, Uppercut, NKnee, Thrust, Reverse 
#R(Phoenix)#e Fire Ball  - Uppercut, NSweep, Lowkick, Lowkick, NKnee, Lowkick#n

You can cancel your combo anytime by using the #wskid#n command.
~

0 SCROLLS~
Long ago, when the Grandmaster Goshen came over to the West, he brought with him #wThe Ninja#n
#wScrolls#n.  These scrolls were passed on to him by his master, the late Grandmaster Wu Cheng.
Goshen used the scrolls in which to teach the ninjas the spirit of being one with the shadow. The
scrolls were held to be the greatest possession of Goshen and his society of ninjas and many
would die before an outsider could see what is written on those precious parchments.  However,
only one outsider has seen the scrolls and has provided us with what he has learned.

SEE HELP '#sBASIC SCROLL#n' '#sKAZENOGAKU SCROLL#n' '#sOMIZUNOGAKU SCROLL#n'
~

