#R=[==========================================================>
#eKakusu            - Become one with the shadows.
Alert             - Sense those who are in the immediate vicinity.
Hakiznetu         - Use your shadow to initiate a sneak attack at will.
Parting Blow      - This allows a ninja to to hit a fleeing opponent. ( Auto )
First Strike      - ALWAYS get first attack against non-ninjas! ( Auto )
#R=[==========================================================>#n
SEE ALSO HELP 'KAZENOGAKU SCROLL' 'OMIZUNOGAKU SCROLL'
~

0 KAZENOGAKU SCROLL~
#R=[==========================================================>
#eAssassinate       - A Deadly backstab from the shadows.
TombonoHiku       - Improved dodging capabilities when blinded. ( Auto )
Caltrops          - Make invisible, poisonous needles used to slow down chasers.
HishokenSlam      - A powerful throw used mainly to get away from the attacker
#R=[==========================================================>#n
SEE ALSO HELP 'BASIC SCROLL' 'OMIZUNOGAKU SCROLL'
~

0 OMIZUNOGAKU SCROLL~
#R=[==========================================================>
#eTunnel            - Disappear under the ground temporary dodging your victim's attack. ( Auto )
Illusion          - Creates a dummy to act as a decoy.
Finale Chance     - Receives a last chance to survive your defeat. ( Auto )
#R=[==========================================================>#n
SEE ALSO HELP 'BASIC SCROLL' 'KAZENOGAKU SCROLL'
~

