0 MONEY BANK~
.
   Savage Wars: Good Ol' Days have done away with questing
and quest points and now use a monetary system with #ygold and #esilver#n
pieces.
   #w1 million #esilver pieces#n are worth #w1 #ygold piece#n and you get
#esilver pieces#n from killing mobs.
   However, only #ygold pieces#n are used in the business world so you have
to stock up on these to buy items which you may need, like a house, 
class equipment etc.

   Note though that they are squadrons and thieves who will like nothing
better but to steal your money. Hence, you should go to one of the various
banks in the land and deposit all of your gold pieces for safekeeping
( i.e #pdepositgold#n ). When you want money for some reason, likewise use
the #pwithdrawgold#n command. These commands can ONLY be done in banks.
~

