-0 WARP TRAVEL~
.
   This can be used to return back to the Crystal Cathedral if you are lost in a town
and kingdom etc and can't recall. Note that this can't be done with a fight timer.

   Travel is a command you can used to travel to players and mobs throughout the land
providing you don't have a fight timer.
~

0 AUTOCLASS DETOX~
.
   Use #eautoclass#n at the healer to choose what class you want to go into.

   Use #Pdetox#n at the healer to declass. As it is a gift from the gods, you will lose
most of your stats and legend when doing so.
~

0 BET~
.
   Players have the chance to place bets on arena fights. If you win, you will
get twice the money that is bet on otherwise you will lose all.

Syntax - Bet (amount) (player)

   Sometimes, an arena match may be a secret bonus match and betters ahave a
chance of winning great prizes like coin tokens, rank tokens etc.
~

0 SOUNDS~
.
   #wSyntax - #gSound #yon#g/#yoff#n

   If your mud-client is MSP compatible, you have the option of listening to BackGround
Music and Sound Effects on Savage Wars: Utopia. Just download the files at the site given
below and put them in your sound directory for your client. Then use the Sound command
to turn on music.
   Likewise if you don't want to hear any music or if your mud-client isn't MSP compatible,
use the Sound command again to turn it off.

   Special Thanks to Jobo for providing not only some of the sound files used on his site,
but for also providing useful tips, snippets and information on his Dystopia Mud Series.

   Music can be download at - http://hutopia.n3.net or http://www.geocities.com/hutopia2001/
~

0 'PARADOX AND RANGE' RETALIATION~
.
#eNote that normal classes can't attack Ultra classes and vice versa.#n

If you cap a character who is out of your range then you get auto paradoxed.

#wThe cap range is #z#y5#n #wpkills if the victim is under 20 pkills.#n

Meaning someone with 5 pkills can cap someone with 0 pkills and above.
 
Someone with 10 pkills can cap 5 pkills and onwards.

#zThere is no range for capping above your pkills!#n

A 0 pkills person can cap a 1 pkills person.

A 11 pkills person can cap a 40 pkills person.

#wThe cap range is #z#y10#n #wpkills if the victim is 20 - 39 pkills.#n

#wThe cap range is #z#y20#n #wpkills if the victim is over 39 pkills.#n

There is an exception to this rule however in certain situations. If you get
attacked by someone out of your range, you can #wretaliate#n on them. Basically,
this means you can decapitate them without fear of being paradoxed. However, you
won't get anything for the kill either.
~

0 CLONES 'DARK KNIGHTS' SORCERORS~
.
   In the cold depths of a hidden labotary stands two powerful men, both cloaked
in highly sophisicated clothings. Their agenda for this meeting is highly
classified, although the reasons are clear.
   #e"We shouldn't had trusted them..."#n the first one said, his eyes barely visible
above the furry neck guard.
   #L"Yes... but now isn't the time to drivel..."#n the other replied as he moves the
tendrils of his armor with a sly flick of his wrist. #L"It is time we show the traitors
the true power of Nests Cartel."#n
   #e"Understood... Release the clones now Zero?"#n
   #L"Indeed Krizalid... Indeed..."#n

   Created with the sole purpose of destruction and world dominance, these beings are
granted abilities from the DNA of the world's greatest heroes and villians. Staring
into those cold, merciless eyes, it seems that they had forsaken the path of good...
thus preferring to stay in this new hell forever...

   #wSEE ALSO: HELP #LCLONE-ATTRIBUTES, CLONE-STYLES, CLONE-MADNESS#n
~

