0 FORBIDDEN-STYLE~
.
   Most of Nests' effort was to obtain any samples or records of the being
known as Astayanax Destrega. Master of the sword and knowledge, this grim
young man always expolited weaknesses to eradicate the foe. What was truly
amazing in this subject's case is the sheer capabilities of Renzokuken...
   Now however, with the brilliance of Nests Cartel, samples of his DNA is
fused into their clones... thus giving Zero and Krizalid that extra step to
World Dominance.

#eAdvise        - #wBeing perfect tacticians, the Dark Ones can quickly tilt
                the favours to a person. (#e20 pkills#w)
#eAntiStock     - #wUse your dark powers to prevent anyone from gaining stock
                in the room for a duration. (#e25 pkills#w)
#ePsychic Shift - #wWith perfect knowledge of the barrier comes the power to
                dodge massive attacks. (#e30 pkills#w)
#eLionHeart     - #wBy focusing on their intelligence, Dark Ones can now use
                Renzokuken as a Level 5 equip skill as well. (#e30 pkills#w)

#wSEE ALSO: HELP #LCLONE-DESPERATION, 'FORBIDDEN-COMBO', 'FORBIDDEN-MAGIC'#n
~

0 'FORBIDDEN-MAGIC'~
.
#eAnalysis        - #wThe masters of Knowledge, Dark Knights and now clones
                  can use the victim's fears and thoughts against them. (#eAnalyse#w)
#eDetermine       - #wThe masters of Knowledge, Dark Knights and now clones
                  can study attacks and come up with the best way to counter them. (#eDetermine#w)
#eDark Bomb       - #wStagger a victim with a powerful blast of dark energy. (#eDarkbomb#w)
#eHyper           - #wMake a target recover from their most powerful moves quicker. (#eHyper#w)
#eSword Rain      - #wUnleash a barrage of swords to a victim in the vicinity. (#eSwordrain#w)
#eMergance        - #wBelievers of fair combat, make 'vulturers' pay for their sins with
                  one of the most feared spells banned from the Holy Church. (#eMergance#w)
#eHeaven's Wrath  - #wUnleash a blast of shocking energy across the vicinity. (#eHwrath#w)
#eShadow Stitch   - #wNo battle is safe from the dark ones... (#eStitch#w)
#ePsychic Barrier - #wSurround all allies with a powerful damage absorbing barrier.
                  (#ePsychicbarrier#w) (#eNon Remort only#w)
#eAbsolute Zero   - #wUse the powers of frost to shiver the bones of all foes. (#eAbsoluteZero#w)
#eUndying Faith   - #wNot even hell can stop a master of the dark sword from their task. (#eAuto#w)#n
~

