0 MAGICSWORD-STYLE~
.
   Luc Nihil was without a doubt the greatest warrior from the eastern lands.
Capable of fusing magic with mortal blades, she single handingly stopped her
country from being invaded over and over again. But such was her powers that
there were no successors to take her place... and thus these mystical arts
were gone.
   Now however, with the brilliance of Nests Cartel, samples of her DNA is
fused into their clones... thus giving Zero and Krizalid that extra step to
World Dominance.

#wMani Katti - #LLegendary sword that gives infinite mana for a duration. #p(20 pkills)
#wSol Katti  - #LThe unknown 'heroic' sword that is the brother of the Durandal... #p(30 pkills)

#wSEE ALSO: HELP #LCLONE-DESPERATION, 'SWORDS OF DARKNESS', 'SWORDS OF FIRE',
          'SWORDS OF EARTH', 'SWORDS OF ICE', 'SWORDS OF THUNDER', 'SWORDS OF MOON'#n
~

0 CLONE-DESPERATION~
.
   Even when all seems lost, the Assassins are given chances to make a glorious
comeback. By focusing on the damage they sustain, they can use this to harness
their anger; raising it to the point where they can unleash a devastating
attack or storing it for even more power.

   #wSEE ALSO: HELP #LMAGICS-DESPERATION, DARK-DESPERATION#n
~

0 MAGICS-DESPERATION~
.
#RMagiwall - #CDampen all magical attacks onto yourself temporary by using your
           sword's spiritual energy as a shield.
           #yRequirements : ( Auto - Low Health )

#RRageDash - #CBy summoning all the heat around him, the Assassin can temporary
           raise his anger to perform a devastating scorching attack.
           #yRequirements : 1 Stock ( Levels ) ( Direct Attack )

#eDespairStrike - #COnly with the power of the Void can sorcerors take away the
                life saving skills of their enemies with this rapid slash.
                #yRequirements : 2 Stock ( Levels ) ( Direct Attack )

#CPiercingOne - #CRain the entire vicinity with a barrage of spiritual swords
              and watch your foes scream in sheer agony.
              #yRequirements : 3 Stock ( Levels ) ( Area Attack )

#oMoonslash - #CA powerful multi-hit strike that can leave opponents reeling!
            #yRequirements : 3 Stock ( Levels ) ( Direct Attack )
~

0 'SWORDS OF DARKNESS'~
.
   Nicknamed the School of Despair, this school came to bout from a regenade sorceror
who sold his very soul for supremcy of the Dark Sword. For years, villages had lived
in sheer terror until he was killed by the Dark Knights. Now with his knowledge left
back, aspiring sorcerors now have the chance to follow in his footsteps to truly
master the Sword. Now assassin, these skills are yours to behold.

   The magicks, or swords if you will, learn in this school are:

#eDarkSword       - #wAssassins can use this demonic ability from the dark sorceror to
                  strike Fear to the followers of Good.
#eChaosSword      - #wA disruptive sword ability Assassins can use to wear down their foes.
#eDemonic Revenge - #wEven in their defeat, Assassins can place a deadly curse on their
                  foes in the wake of their demise. #P( Auto )
#eDeathField      - #wA chaotic field of unknown origins, it can do a variety of disruptive
                  things and it kills at will...#n
~

0 'SWORDS OF MOON'~
.
   Nicknamed the School of Luna, this school is the only representation of the Goddess'
direct intervention with mere mortals. Helping Valerie and Lucatix saving the world from 
a untold danger, she as well as the techniques taught to the young sorceror faded 
away for eons. But now they were recovered and taught again to the masters of the
Sword. Now assassin, these skills are yours to behold.

   The magicks, or swords if you will, learn in this school are:

#yMoonSword      - #wWith a splash of Luna energy, the Assassin can creates a vacuum with their
                 sword draining health from their foes.
#yQuadraSlice    - #wA powerful multi-hit slice which drains the victim's mana.
#yHand Swayrance - #wAssassin can use this technique to quickly dash towards their foes blocking
                 their hits with their free hand. #P( Auto )
#yLunaBeam       - #wBy concentrating on the Moon energy around them, Assassin can use their
                 sword to emit a deadly beam that drains life from all foes in the room; restoring
                 their friends' health along with theirs.
~

0 'SWORDS OF FIRE'~
.
   Nicknamed the School of Wrath, this school dedicates it students to the offensive
nature of Fire, allowing the young Sorcerors to forge their techniques into powerful
attacks. Now assassin, these skills are yours to behold.

   The magicks, or swords if you will, learn in this school are:

#RFireWall      - #wA more powerful version of Fireshield, The Assassin whirls his sword around his
                body, creating raving fire which will burns anyone who attacks him.
#RFireSword     - #wFocusing all the energy onto his blade, An Assassin can disrupt a victim with
                a powerful upperstrike, usually setting them on fire.
#RDancingFlames - #wFocusing all the energy onto his blade, An Assassin can unleash a devastating
                fireball onto the room, burning everything in their path.
#RExplosion     - #wGiving up a partial amount of energy, an Assassin using this skill can set his
                blade on fire, allowing it to sears a person's flesh with a mystical flame. (Auto)#n
~

0 'SWORDS OF ICE'~
.
   Nicknamed the School of Protection, this school dedicates it students to the defensive
nature of Ice, allowing the young Sorcerors to forge their techniques into useful
attacks. Now assassin, these skills are yours to behold.

   The magicks, or swords if you will, learn in this school are:

#LAuraWave  - #wBy rapdily twirling his blade around his body, an Assassin can create a wave
            of energy which heals all in the room.
#LIceSword  - #wBy adjusting the temperature around him, the Assassin can deliver a powerful
            blow that may freeze an enemy temporary.
#LIceWall   - #wSplitting his sword into hundrends of images, An Assassin can barred all 
            horizontal exits that directing the swords towards them, forming a deadly
            barrier which will hurt anyone trying to pass through them.
#LFrigidcut - #wCharging up his sword with magical energy, an Assassin can smash his sword
            through the very ground he stands, turning it into a glacier of ice. All
            movement on this slippery ground will be impossible unless the person in
            question is flying.#n
~

0 'SWORDS OF THUNDER'~
.
   Nicknamed the School of Cunning, this school dedicates it students to the multiple
abilities of Lightning, allowing the young Sorcerors to forge their techniques into useful
attacks. Now assassin, these skills are yours to behold.

   The magicks, or swords if you will, learn in this school are:

#yBlitzSword   - #wSummoning all of the electricty around him, the Assassin can deliver a
               power strike which may drains the victim's mana and movements.
#yThunderBeam  - #wRedirecting the electrons to the tip of his blade, the Assassin can emit
               a powerful beam which strikes everyone in the room.
#yBlitzTouch   - #wMoving like a lightning bolt, the Assassin's dodge rate is GREATLY improved, but
               at a tremedous price.
#yBlitzStrike  - #wMoving like the very wind, an Assassin with the knowledge of this skill has
               a GREATER chance of hitting the opponent. However, due to the complicated
               nature of this skill, this usually tires the Assassin out quickly.#n
~

0 'SWORDS OF EARTH'~
.
   Nicknamed the School of Patience, this school dedicates it student the sheer might of
the Earth, allowing young Sorcerors to forge their techniques into devastating attacks.
However, since the Sorcerors did not appreciate this school compare to the others, it
isnot as developed but is still very, very dangerous. Now assassin, these skills are yours
to behold.

   The magicks, or swords if you will, learn in this school are:

#gEarthFist  - #wUtilizing the power of the Earth, the Assassin can increase the power of their
             blows. ( Auto )
#gEarthSword - #wDrawing Strength from the Earth, the Assassin can execute a swirling strike
             draining its victim's stamina.
#gEarthGrasp - #wBy using the powers of Gaia, Assassins can pull back weakened foes for the kill.
#gRockBlast  - #wFocusing his magick from his sword, the Assassin can bring the very Earth beneath 
             his feet alive, striking his foes at will.#n
