0 CLONE-MADNESS~
.
   Loving a challenge, Assassins seek out the best challengers in the world to test
their skills against with. Unlike most people who fuel their anger and power through their
rage, Assassins' lifeforce is obtained this way and is required for them to execute their
powerful techniques, the more in touch with their rage they are, the more powerful they 
are. However, Assassins must keep their rage in check as if it becomes to low,
they will lost their mind completely and die from an unbelievable sense of docility.
~

0 HIGHWIND~
.
Judgement day comes and you step towards your final destination.
Strolling into the depth of the northern cave you wonder to yourself,
'what the "$&^& have i left myself in for' and 'I'm really too old for this
$%^&Ł'.
  Being part of the Highwind family you clutch your spear and dive in head
first into the unknown.
  Your name is Cid Highwind. Your age is 32. Your occupation is a pilot.
And your weapon is your trusty spear. Of course, no one can forget your
cigarette.

#CSkills the Highwind receives:

  #cDragtalk  - #CHighwind's communication channel.
  #cJump      - #CSoar high into the sky... then land onto a victim within the area.
  #cUltraJump - #CAn enhanced jump attack with even longer range.
  #cImpale    - #CImpale your foe, preventing them from fleeing.
  #cVSpears   - #CA series of deadly attacks to stagger your victim.

#wSEE ALSO: HELP #C'LIMIT BREAKS'#w, #C'HIGHWIND-ATTRIBUTES'#n
~

0 'LIMIT BREAKS'~
.
In the game FF7 by Squaresoft, Cid have limit breaks that can
only be achieved after taking a large amount of damage. Of course the limits
are based on Cid Highwind from FF7. But the way you can execute the attacks
in Utopia is determined by what groove you pick.

#CDesperation Attacks#n

#cWhiskeyBreak - #CHave you ever encountered Cid when he is drunk?
Well now is your chance... #w(level 1)

#cDynamite - #CLight some dynamite with your cigerette and go smokin'! #w(level 1)
  
#cDragon - #CSummon a dragon to rush to your aid! #w(level 2)

#cHyperJump - #CA super cool jump which explodes upon impact. #w(level 2)

#cDragonDive - #CA chance skill of hitting the enemy many times and causing
instant death. #w(level 2)

#cDragoon Throw - #CJump into the air and shower your opponent with spears.
#w(level 3)

#cHighwind - #CCall your highwind to do a mass amount of damage on your enemy,
like a weapon of mass destruction. #w(level 3)#n
~

