0 SAIYA-JINS SAIYANS~
.
   Saiya-Jins are a warrior races from the planet Vegita. They have a unbridled love 
of fighting as well as any challenge. Usually Saiya-Jin are a very pride filled 
people and refuse to walk away from a fight. #wThey are born with a monkey like tail 
that gives them to transform into a giant ape like creature every time they see 
the full moon.#n If there tail is cut off they loose this ability and will revert back 
to normal however tail can grow back up to the age of 12. Saiya-Jin also have the 
ability to go "Super Saiya-Jin" during which time there hair stands on end and turns 
yellow while their eyes turn blue. It is a skill that requires a pure heart to 
accomplish and a lot of will power.
   For a while, they were used by a powerful alien force to raid and plunger planets
for priracy means but eventually Vegita was destroyed and the Saiya-Jins were thought
to be lost.
   Now, in this age of confusion, they have return to continue where they have left
off, fight nonstop...

#wSEE ALSO: HELP CHARGING, 'EYE SCOUTER', SAIYANPOWERLEVEL,
            SAIYANTECHNIQUE, SAIYAN-ATTRIBUTES, 'SAIYAN LIMITS'#n
~

0 'SAIYAN-ATTRIBUTES'~
.
#RAdvantages

#y- #RMasters of the fist
#y- #RHave a wide arrangement of deadly techniques
#y- #RSaiyan Powerlevel increases with more p-kills#n

#RDisadvantages

#y- #RChances are fleeing from battle are grim...#n
~

0 SAIYANPOWERLEVEL~
.
   The essence of a true Saiya-jin. True abilities of a Saiyan is based on his
or her powerlevel. The higher it is, the better in combat he/she is against other
Saiya-jins as well as having the capacity of doing the more powerful Saiyan Techniques.

   You can vigorously train your powerlevel by fighting worthy opponents.
~

0 'EYE SCOUTER'~
.
   Saiya-Jins, from the beginning of times, have used a powerful device which their wear
on their left eye, an eye scouter. With this device, they can use a variety of commands
which are:

#CPOWERREAD <victim>    - #cReads the victim powerlevel and stats.
#CPOWERSEARCH <victim>  - #cSearches the World for a victim by zooming in on their powerlevel.
#CCOMMUNICATE <message> - #cAllows you to speak with other saiyans throughout the world.

#wNote you have to be wearing the eye scouter to use these skills or they wont work.#n
~

0 SAIYANTECHNIQUE~
.
   Dued to their lust for fighting, Saiya-Jins have developed a variety of techniques
which they can used in battle. It is up to you one way or the other to relearn the lost
skills and make Son Goku and Vegeta proud of you...

#CBigBang        - #cVegeta's favourite attack.
#CKamehameha     - #cThe Kame Master favourite attack.
#CKaioken        - #cAn ancient technique used to increase one's strength.
#CTaiyouken      - #cA blinding technique with various uses.
#CKienzan        - #cA powerful energy disc that can cut off limbs.
#CKakusan        - #cStrike everyone in the vicinity with energy balls.
#CMouthblast     - #cThe Ultimate Oozaru attack.
#CTailSwipe      - #cOozaru attack
#CScatterPunch   - #cOozaru attack
#CPounce         - #cOozaru attack
#CSSj            - #cTransform yourself into a Super Saiya-jin.
#CPowerball      - #cTransforms yourself into an Oozaru at will. #w(10 Pkills)
#CChouKamehameha - #cThe Ultimate Kamehameha. #w(20 Pkills)
~

