0 SAMURAIS~
.
   The Army of the True Emperor, Samurais were borned to follow and uphode the Code of 
Bushido. When the Acopalyse had arrived, the Samurais chosen to stay on their island 
and live their peaceful lives. This however, had changed one day when a group of 
Ninjas had invaded the country and assassinated the Emperor.
   Now without their leader, the Samurais vowed revenge for his shameful death at all 
costs.

#cAmaztalk       - #LSamurai's communication channel

#wSEE ALSO: HELP 'SAMURAI COMBAT', 'KATANA SKILLS', SAMURAI-ATTRIBUTES, 'SAMURAI LIMITS'#n
~

0 'SAMURAI COMBAT'~
.
   By connecting their chi force within their blade, Samurais are capable of executing
devastating combos that will pummel their foes to the ground.

   In fights, Samurais can do one of three basic attacks with can be combine to make
bigger attacks. These attacks are: Light Slash, Medium Slash and Hard Slash 
   Each of these attacks cost a certain amount of chi ( Light Slash - 1, Medium Slash
- 2, Hard Slash - 3 ) and at thus, Samurais are only limited to a certain amount of
attacks per round this way.

   By combining their strikes in certain orders, they will eventually be able to execute 
#yDeath Blows#n. A Death Blow is a combo finisher that does much more damage than an 
average strike.

To see the available death blows to you, type #wknowledge#n. For example, you may see something
like this:

   Earth Dance  :  #w(7)#n LS, LS, MS, HS             #y[100%]#n
   Crystal Water:      HS, MS, MS, LS, HS, MS, LS #y[ 47%]#n

   The numbers in circle brackets represent how much chi the technique costs while the
numbers in square brackets represent how much of the technique you know already.

   The symbols inbetween are this:

             #pHS - Hard Slash  #CMS - Medium slash  #wLS - Light Slash#n

   Therefore, to be able to learn Crystal Water, one will keep on having to enter the
command list there repeatively until it gets to 100%. The next time one do the combo after
that, they will perform the Death Blow, Crystal Water.
~

0 'SAMURAI LIMITS'~
.
#CCombo     - #yUnleash a barrage of random strikes at your foe. #w(Level 1 - 3)
#yMasamune  - #CThe ultimate sdraw spirit attack from the infamous Samurai Warrior. #w(Level 2)
#CQuickLash - #yMake your opponent's eyes bulge in surprise at the speed of this attack. #w(Level 3)
~

0 'KATANA SKILLS'~
.
   It was rumored that there exists legendary katana blades, with contains the souls of their
wielders. Some of the best Samurai in history - Muramasa, Masamune and others possessed
powerful katana blades capable of deadly attacks. With their deaths, they had passed their
skills to the very katana blades which can be drawn out and used by other Samurais.
To draw out the soul from a mystical Katana Blade requires alot of magical energy to
accomplish and be forewarn, this very action may cause the katana blade in question to 
shatter.
   The Legendary Katana Blades are:

#cTurana, #cKi-jira, #LMuramasa#n

What each of them is capable of are unknown at this point dued to the secretive native of the 
legendary katanas...
~

