0 'DARK DRAGOON'~
.
   Being the most mysterious of all the elements, no one know the origins of the #eDark Dragon#n.
However, they are well known for their disruptive attacks used to weaken opponents as the Dark
Dragoons move in for the kill.

#y _______         ___________       _____________
#y/ #wMAGIC #y\_______/ #wAttribute #y\_____/ #wDescription #y\________________________________
