#y| #CLastPrayer    #y| #g (2)         #y| #gA damning curse that SEVERELY affects a victim.   #y|
#y| #eDarkDragon    #y| #g (3)         #y| #gSummon the Legendary Dark Dragon.                 #y|
#y|_______________________________________________________________________________/#n
~

0 'JADE DRAGOON'~
.
   Being the most defensive of all the elements, the #gJade Dragon#n has great stamina and
power, fighting long after all other dragons crumble to the ground in exhaustion. As such, Jade
Dragoons like protecting themselves from various forms of attacks while hammering powerful
ones of their own onto their foes.

