0 'HOLY DRAGOON'~
.
    Not as powerful nor as resourceful as the other elements, the #wWhite Silver Dragon#n
specializes in healing and holy attacks; aiding fallen dragons and restoring their wounds
much quickly than possible in their war against their enemies.

