0 'SEA DRAGOON'~
.
   The #LBlue Sea Dragon#n is an ancient dragon who sees the need of having restoring and 
attacking magic and as such, spent ages learning some. In battle, Sea Dragons can be fairly
useful as they can either attack the foes or heal their members; sometimes doing both.

