0 DRAGOONSPECIAL~
.
   Like knights, dragoons also work better in groups. However being part of a higher system of
evolution, the Dragoons must group their respective subparts together and fight gracefully in
battle. Once there is 3 or more different Dragoon type ( e.g Fire, Water, Holy ), the leader
of the group can use the #PShift#n command, transforming everyone into dragoons while sending
them into a special plane like area where noone can flee.
   In this plane, all dragoon attributes are improved and will remained so until the leader
comes out of dragoon form.
~

0 'ELEMENTAL BEINGS'~
.
Elemental beings are beigns that can either defend themselves from various forms of elemental attacks
or attack viciously with a elemental attack. They are as follows:
#0Hob#7bit
#gDuergar
#CSnow Elf
#RPhoenix
#yWisp#n

#CWINDTALK       - Elemental Communication Channel#n

SEE ALSO: HELP 'HOBBIT', HELP 'DUERGAR', HELP 'SNOW ELVES', HELP 'PHOENIX', HELP 'WISP'
                   HELP 'ELEMENTAL-ATTRIBUTES'
~

0 'ELEMENTAL-ATTRIBUTES'~
.
#LAdvantages

#0- #RHobbits are adept at dark and holy attacks
#0- #RHobbits have a good resistance against dark and holy attacks.
#0- #RNon Hobbits heal from attacks of the same elemental type as them.
#0- #RDuergars are adept at earth attacks
#0- #RSnow elf's are adept at ice attacks
#0- #RPhoenix's are adept at fire attacks
#0- #RWisp's are adept at thunder attacks
#0- #RDon't need summon counters to summon there deity
#0- #RUseless using an aligned elemental deity against them.

#LDisadvantages

#L- #0Don't have a choice in a deity
#L- #0Can't remort, and personality and deities are set.
#L- #0Some skills are restricted use either by pk's or generation.
#L- #0They suffer what there deities are weak to
~

0 HOBBIT~
.
In a far distant land many a persons life is controlled by one mere ring.. Everyone who touch or see this
ring feel the great desire to wear it and once they do a great time of darkness shatters the world that
everyone stands on. This one very ring is filled with the seven deadliest sins known to any being, greed,
gluttony, etc. One day a brave and fearless Hobbit named Frodo Baggins takes up the job of destroying this
ring, if you are a Hobbit, can you one day become a lord of a ring? What do you choose.. To wear it.. or not
to wear it? #wGood#n .. or #0evil#n?

#0Hobbyarmor       #7- #0Create your hobbit eq and your trusty ring
#7Siren            #0- #7When not wearing the ring, you place your trust in Siren. #w(10 pkills)
#0Diablos          #7- #0When wearing the ring, evil consumes you and you trust Diablos. #w(10 pkills)

#CSEE ALSO: HELP #w'HOLY HOBBIT', #e'EVIL HOBBIT', #C'LORD RINGHOLDER', #y'HOBBIT LIMITS'#n
~

0 'HOLY HOBBIT'~
.
Being free of the ring a Hobbit can execute many different commands that can aid him in his battle against
the forces of evil.

#CPetite Angel    #7- #CIncrease your parry and dodge. ( Auto )
#CGods Shine      #7- #CAs you get weaker God may intervene to plant your escape. ( Auto )
#CGrand Love      #7- #CShow your foe the greatest in love.
#CTruthful        #7- #CExplain the truth to your foe destroying there faith.
#CTilly Mint      #7- #CBe the cutest you can be to devestate the attacker.
#CFamed Archangel #7- #CA spell of secrets, no one really knows how this affects you.
#CLoath Demon     #7- #CA demon detector, again, no one knows how it works.
~

