.
As a Hobbit trains with the use of his ring he eventually becomes powerful enough to master the ring and
learn the ultimate techniques that can be used whether he wields the ring or not.

#CCrystalDreams    #7- #CShatter every dream in existance for the enemy
#CThe Happy Hobbit #7- #CHappiness consumes you and you improve your way of fighting (Auto)
#CFrogget          #7- #CTurn your enemy into a frog disabling there timers.
#CWraithe Knight   #7- #CSummon Wraithe Knights to do your bidding, but be weary, it drains you of other
                         powers.
