0 'DUERGARS'~
.
Ugly and tiny you are. A dwarf like creature with a giant beard, and this is the
women we are talking about. Closely related to the dwarfs you inherit most abilities of
a usual dwarf. Duergars are strong like there distant cousins but they have been tainted
with #0evil#n, making them almost closely related to #0Lloth and her Drow Kin#n. You are masters
of the #0shadows#n and NOTHING can get past your vision in the same area as you, as you are
adept to the #0shadows#n and the #gground#n the only thing that will surpass your vision is
distant #0hidden#n #L***#0Ass#rass#0ins#L***#n in the #qwilderness#n far away. Also,
because of your time #0underground#n no Drow will be able to fool you with there #0darkness#n.
   Unlike the dwarfs you were feuding with a long time ago in history you are used to
#grocks and stone#n, you're also not scared of #Lwater#n due to living close to many
many #Loceans#n around the #0evil underground caves#n.

#gTitan        #y- #gSummon your Deity Titan to aid you in battle #w(10 pkills).

#ySEE ALSO: #gHELP 'DUERGAR SKILLS', 'INNATE DUERGAR', 'DUERGAR LIMITS'#n
~

