.
#CSnow Elves#n are very thin and tall individuals who reside in #Csnowy #qmountains#n. From spending so much
time in the #Ccold#n they are adept to the winter and to the #7snow#n. Also because of spending so much time
in the #Ccold#n they have learnt how to master its #Pmysterious #0arts#n.
   #CSnow Elves#n aren't liked by other #qElves#n and are rejected mostly like how #0Drow#n where rifted apart
from the #qWood Elves#n. #CSnow Elves#n are adept in the ways of the #qbow#n and they especially like to
use #Lice#n in their technique of the #qbow#n. #CSnow Elves#n are resiliant creatures who are adept in the
arts of #7magic, #Pmelee#n and #qarchery#n. Even though the #CSnow Elves#n are kind creatures compared to their
cousin #0Drow#n they reject all forms of Elven armor, as time went by, they felt to split themselves apart
further and further from their original Elven kin. They are a force to be reckoned with on Utopia and can 
