0 'SHADOW WARRIORS'~
No one know their very reason of existence, but it is these elite warriors
that were responsible for the original downfall of the Ninja Clan. Rumoured
to be warriors of the Shadow Goddess, these merciless figures were a fatal
gift to the GrandMaster. Now in this time and aid, they had mysterious
appear again to kill at will...

#eCommands for Shadow Warriors are:

    #y* #eMiktalk                 - #yshadow warrior communication channel

#eSEE: #y'HERITAGE OF THE SHADOWS', 'RAGE OF THE INNER DEMON', SHADOW-ATTRIBUTES,
     'RAGE LIMITS' #eand #y'STYLE OF THE DRUNKEN MASTER'#n
~

0 SHADOW-ATTRIBUTES~
.
   #y#uBonuses#n

#e- #yMasters of the Shadow Plane
#e- #yMost of their skills are enhanced in the Realm of the Shadows

   #y#uDisadvantages#n

#e- #yWeak out of Shadow Plane
~

