0 DAYWALKER~
.
A half breed, a perfect race and bestowed with the strengths of both races. Daywalkers
age very slowly hence living long than humans and almost as long as true blood vampires. 
Through their lifetime, daywalkers learns the fighting skills and mystical powers of both races.  
Below is a list of powers harnessed by a daywalker.

#e* Inquest       - #CLearn Daywalker Abilities.
#e* Insight       - #CGet info on all the abilities you had learned.#n

#eSEE ALSO: #CHELP 'DAYWALKER-ATTRIBUTES', 'DAYWALKER LIMITS'#n
~

0 'DAYWALKER LIMITS'~
.
